F\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?ndfem so f\u233?t\u233? k\u225?njo yarametam Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio efghon f\u233?feyot. Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m mbark\u225?nd t\u233?feyot m\u233?n\u225?t wafrogh\u233?t, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233? nanote ndimbale a uw\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u225?yaf\u233? m\u233?inyotio f\u233?m em \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?t nanote ndimbale. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?nd y\u233?ndio mere f\u233?fenem\u233?n m\u233? n\u233?ngorayam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n. Y\u233?nd m\u233? n\u233?ngorayam mere ndern\u225?ye ende f\u233?mofem ewaindati a efalo ey\u225?totai m\u233?inyotio was\u233?rmbogh a t\u233?kr\u225?t f\u233?mofem \u225?rk\u233? efandati.
