Ng\u225?nj\u225?n siy\u233?m mbark\u225?nd: Y\u233?mon so ekmete k\u233?rtayan f\u225? emofem t\u233?kr\u225?tan ekmetat f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
A Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tawaramang\u233? enagh f\u233?feyot efe f\u233?m t\u233? tam t\u233?kr\u225?tan, a t\u233?feyot nden\u233?yameyo. Y\u233?mon so yafrote y\u233?n\u233? t\u225?f njam Yur\u233? Yesu kufarng\u233? k\u233?tam\u233? njafarta y\u225?njo muy\u233? k\u233?r ro njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rf\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
f\u233?s arangaf\u233?, m\u233?n\u225?t t\u233?kr\u225?tan s\u225?i t\u225?kmang\u233? f\u225? emofem t\u233?kenat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a f\u225? emofem yau k\u225?y\u225?retat mer si t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesuenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u225? so ambino t\u233?kr\u225?tan t\u225?kmang\u233? tuot, tafalong\u233? k\u233?tam\u233? Yurata a y\u225?njo ndimbal kwayagh\u233? waftata. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Njam f\u225? n\u233?nangota s\u225?i tanang\u233? ndimbal kwayagh\u233?, a uyogh y\u225?njo efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r tamb\u233?n. F\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? so em y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem efalo yiy\u225?totati n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? ewaufroy\u233?m y\u225?nem\u233?n.
