Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, y\u233?nd m\u233? noraiwam Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? f\u233?feyot nden\u233? t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so ey\u225?tote efalo gh\u233?rsayan k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?ndan y\u233?mon emotai f\u233?m. Y\u233?nd noraiwam Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so y\u225?njo waftaye ewafrote m\u233?inyotio f\u233?fene m\u233?nde a ndimbal mwigham\u233?n wafroghyam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, \u225?r\u233?m so yuyotat Yur\u233? Yesuene y\u233?tkw\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m ndern\u225?ye emor. W\u233?i f\u233?mofem so yuyotati, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m Yesuene em. Y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio afr\u225?taye em m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene a Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisoene ng\u225?r\u225?mm\u233?n.
