Yau m\u233? nasambnetati o n\u233?w\u233?rsotati y\u233?fenem\u233?n efe n\u233?ngafrotat nden\u233? Yurane angogh t\u233? nufar. Yau t\u225?f efalo ey\u225?totati f\u225? njam n\u233?ngafrotat nden\u233? y\u233?mofem t\u233? t\u233?fandat gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?gh, o ufrogh si, o t\u225?f f\u233?r\u233?n njam t\u233? t\u233?ng\u233?m t\u233?fe tamb\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Yau t\u225?f ewasotat \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m \u225?mb endm\u233?. M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? efogh m\u233? yau so y\u233?n\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?notio ndimbal as\u233?nan\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf a n\u225?kofnar \u225?r so kufarng\u233?, efe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so yas\u233?rmbote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
