Nawafarotati y\u233?ndo ndern\u225?ye tang\u233?mndetan njam y\u233?nd f\u233?maf\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
A f\u233?m mat em n\u233?m\u233? yam f\u225? yangote, m\u233?n\u225?t so k\u233?t\u233? kufarng\u233? y\u225?ne efogh njam kawerang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?kofnaye \u225?s\u225?fogh siy\u233?m \u225?s\u225?foghan y\u233?m kwankwane, a so m\u233? y\u233?m kwankwane k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emo m\u233? y\u233?rete s\u225?i kit\u233?rmbong\u233? y\u233?n\u233? sifayata. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
