Y\u233?n\u233? yaufi \u225?r so y\u233?n\u233?m s\u225?i yafrota \u225?s\u225?fogh S\u225?if\u233?rene uny\u233?gh waftaye a ufarogh yame a s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yame. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?mon so ewafrote f\u233?nat\u233? s\u225?fot uny\u233?gh yam m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i ewasota f\u225? efe em k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?kr\u225?tfaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? kakenaw\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tuwetaw\u233?t a tumyongay\u233?nd efalo \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayan so kunjarngai f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
