Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m efalo si: \u225?r njam m\u233?nde y\u233?m Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t, y\u233?mon so y\u233?kwne mer \u225?s\u225?fogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
A Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r so y\u233?m t\u233?fnofnar; y\u225?ne ay\u233?m \u225?mbiro amaf, awamb\u233?gh yaufiyamta, awamarogh, a mbark\u225?ndro; y\u233?mon aeumyota wan t\u233?fn\u225?r y\u225?njo m\u233?ngot. F\u225? f\u233?yotaro so y\u233?m watamegh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u225? yau so y\u233?m w\u233?ri nu t\u233?fn\u225?r, o \u225?sm\u233?gh \u225?r, w\u233?nde m\u233?tar a krufr\u225?t k\u233?r ro. F\u225? yau t\u225?f y\u233?m mani uw\u233?gh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?mon f\u233?t\u233? aefrenda y\u225?njo m\u233?r\u233?n mere a em\u233?inda y\u225?ne ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i yiy\u225?retat f\u225? m\u233?inyotio utman\u233?ghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
\u193?r ghak\u233?r mat so y\u233?m ndern\u225?ye ewarawene y\u225?njoyo m\u233?r\u233?n. Njam y\u233?mon yau yafrota y\u233?n\u233?, y\u233?mon f\u233?yotarofnar so y\u233?m s\u225?i ewarawene Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r Yesuene m\u233?rnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u225? sotaf\u233? ay\u233?m ndimbal mwighayan, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? yau so tuktukan y\u233?m, a y\u233?mo yau so tanang\u233? t\u233?krat, nden\u233? S\u225?if\u233?r k\u233?s yanai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u225? \u225?r ay\u233?m efe so yut\u233?mndat \u225?r\u233?m Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n t\u233?ndota, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? yau so w\u225?iw\u225?i y\u233?m a k\u225?wamang\u233? S\u225?if\u233?roene ur\u233?ran.
