Dikun nden\u225?yo aem mer wafroghyamaf\u233? aem efalofifi; y\u233?mofem yau so enetat w\u233?ri nu mindefifi o em nit\u233? manian. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u225? so naw\u233?retat efalo sian ndimbal mwigham\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?yaf\u233? kwayagh\u233? emar\u233?ghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u225? f\u233?t\u233? aeufotat fronde, a f\u233?yo njam y\u233?mofem taindangi ufogh yam, f\u225? so n\u225?s\u225?fotat.
