Amaf dikun nden\u233?yameyo mer wafroghyamaf\u233? aem a yau \u225?r waruny\u233?gh amaf aem. F\u225? aem m\u233?tar yamaf\u233? a uny\u233?ghofnar m\u233?inyotio yaman. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Dikun ay\u233?m m\u233? \u225?mbiro amafaf\u233?, a efrenda y\u225?ne ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r a m\u233?r\u233?n merk\u233?r\u225?ye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
