W\u233?nde n\u233?mndafi yau ewafrota ng\u225?nj\u225?nofnar niny\u233? sifaf, \u225?rk\u233? em fifiofnar waitogh\u233?t. Mia f\u233?myo notameta m\u233?n\u225?t ng\u225?nj\u225?n gh\u233?rsat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Fifie awatamegh siy\u233?m \u225?mb merafayo y\u233?m, w\u233?nde mb\u233?rmb\u233?re awatamegh siy\u233?m minde meraf\u233? y\u233?m m\u233?inyotio yam k\u233?nj\u250?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n uny\u233?ghofnar sian gh\u233?rs\u233? ere s\u243?mbio m\u233?n\u225?t s\u233?nonjotau a soram\u233? yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
