Y\u233?nd nasmetam a n\u225?s\u225?fotam taikrataye, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem ekmang\u233?m t\u233?fene m\u233?ghm\u233?gh akegh Ng\u225?nj\u225?n k\u233?nj\u250?n, efe y\u233?m Wanjar\u233?gh \u225?r m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t, a y\u233?fefifi emofem efalo yiy\u225?totat.
