Engwafrota y\u233?n\u233? yam a karam f\u233?myo k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fefaf, m\u233?n\u225?t fene anogh so y\u233?fandat m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
