W\u233?nde yau ekmeta tot\u233?r kwirafene y\u233?tkw\u233?n fefayan; m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fene m\u233?ndeyam njam em\u233?indat f\u225? \u225?r awer\u233?gh\u233?t, y\u233?mofem so tawengongi s\u233?m Kerisoe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? so kamndangi k\u233?rtaf\u233? y\u233?fenjo frondeyo uny\u233?ghofnar sim\u233?n rafar\u233?gh \u225?r y\u225?faf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u225? nden\u233?yame notametat m\u233?n\u225?t efogh ewifotat m\u233?n\u225?yan s\u225?i nawarendat k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? m\u233?ngo k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb m\u233?ngo; w\u233?nde minde m\u225?m\u225?fi siy\u233?m, f\u225? notametat \u225?r waruny\u233?ghan, a \u225?mb \u225?rfene yamfaf s\u225?i enwafnyang, a n\u233?ngorayat \u225?mb yamm\u233?n nden\u233? f\u225? yau so f\u233?t\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, y\u233?nd nemnan nden\u233? tot\u233?r kwir\u233? so \u225?r naweretat kor m\u233?n\u225?t ambumot, a so ewarawenat y\u233?fenjo m\u233?ngon, f\u233?yo nden\u233? yaman yau so erametat \u225?mb f\u233?nef\u233?ne m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?rat m\u233?n\u225?yan s\u225?i n\u233?ngorayat yaufi si t\u233?fenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
\u193?mb kwir\u233? t\u233? nawengoy\u233?nd a S\u225?if\u233?r yaitoy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
W\u233?nde njam \u225?rk\u233? efalo y\u225?togh amafoefaf t\u233? em kwir\u233? y\u225?ne m\u233?rnan, y\u233?mon f\u233?t\u233? so ewarawene a yau so y\u233?fayote k\u233?rt\u233? Yesuene m\u233?rnot, m\u233?n\u225?t Yesuene m\u233?rnam so ew\u225?ut\u225?ne y\u233?n\u233? kwirat efe y\u233?fembia em.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n s\u233?nko \u225?rfenem\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n s\u233?nko \u225?r\u233?m emofem ewafrotat y\u233?fenjo mer \u225?s\u225?fogh nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m so f\u233?t\u233? fai ersat merk\u233?r\u225?ye, m\u233? y\u233?mofemro efe n\u225?s\u225?fotat taikrataye si waitoghan a watameghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Buk si noraye, "Yau kau s\u233?nfneyan tumb\u233? njam kun ndau \u225?s\u225?foghan y\u233?m" a w\u233?ikor '\u193?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u233?m so f\u233?t\u233? ewarametat y\u233?fene fai." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Yau n\u225?y\u225?retati Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n s\u233?nko \u225?roenem\u233?n w\u225?nangogh, t\u225?fandro njam y\u233?n\u233?mnjat s\u243?mbio o nambio gh\u233?kfe fandagh \u225?r\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Njam s\u233?nko \u225?rom yaufiyam yafrota, us\u233?rmbo saf\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?mb \u225?r so em f\u233?rf\u233?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?mndetan y\u233?fene s\u225?fr\u233?re Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a Keriso Yesu a nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r: F\u233?mo t\u225?f merk\u233?r\u225?ye ewaitota si y\u233?nd snorayan fefaf. Njam f\u233?mo ewaitota y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?mo t\u225?f yuyafota \u225?mbiro yam wafrogh k\u233?t\u225?n m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t, f\u233?mo yau t\u225?f yuyafota f\u233?nataye yam wafrogh fene f\u250?tarfefaf a \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
M\u233? yau w\u233?keye em ng\u225?ng\u233? fayogh\u233?t \u225?rfefaf y\u233?fe wategh\u233?t Yurane \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t. Yau kufnya \u225?mb \u225?rfene yaufiyaman, nawarawena f\u233?myo nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Yau nuro so y\u233?nete, w\u233?nde n\u233?mbne w\u233?ri nu so t\u233?neta nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? mur\u233?mur\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n enjne n\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
\u193?mb \u225?rfene yaufiyam em m\u233?inyo fandagh saf\u233?n, a y\u233?fene yaufiyam eng\u233?m fronde moghfaf, w\u233?nde \u225?mb \u225?rfene yaufiyam fandagh\u233?t em soram\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Nden\u233? yameyo mer wafroghyam fandagh\u233?t em m\u233? saf\u233?nro, a nden\u225?yo y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rk\u233? yau em saf\u233?nro yau so atnoghe em.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 6
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
F\u225? efe em efalo y\u225?togh faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r so f\u233?t\u233? merk\u233?r\u225?ye nemnat y\u233?fene yurafenem\u233?n m\u233?inyotio utman\u233?ghaf\u233?, m\u233?n\u225?t efe yau so noraye yaufi si Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene y\u233?tkw\u233?nfaf a t\u233?fene watameghfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Efalo y\u225?togh faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r endefene yur\u233? em efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r yau t\u225?f yuwot efandati, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? w\u233?i em efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r. W\u233?nde f\u225? so f\u233?t\u233? n\u225?s\u225?fotat merk\u233?r\u225?ye, m\u233?nam\u233?n efe eremngote y\u233?fene \u225?s\u225?foghan em efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r efe y\u233?fene uw\u233?ghaf\u233? em.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Uny\u233?gh watamegh a efalo wem\u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?mon so ewatamete a ewawaitota y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Emo njam ewatameta f\u233?natayo si a yau natemnda efalo sifaf t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisoene a watameghfaf t\u233?fene ng\u225?nj\u225?n gh\u233?rsam\u233?n {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
f\u225? sem tuktuk \u225?r em a mat yau em y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n. F\u225? sem wasneng\u233?gh mwighaf\u233? \u233?wigh\u233?t a amrorgh\u233?t sim\u233?n, a y\u233?n\u233? yamam y\u233?n\u233?rse waramnjagh, as\u233?nan\u233?gh, yaufi si oray\u233?gh, m\u233? fayogh, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
a t\u250?m\u233?n \u233?wigh yam en\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rta endefene mer mwigh\u233? yau n\u225?s\u225?fotat a endefaf yau efalo em. F\u225? nemnat nden\u233? ng\u225?nj\u225?n gh\u233?rs\u233? yame kar y\u233?m wem\u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n gh\u233?rsayam minde wem\u225?r y\u233?ny\u225?tote, t\u225?f y\u233?nd fiya t\u233?nremngong\u233? y\u233?n\u233? rokaram n\u233?m\u233? t\u233?fefaf em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndfem en\u233?rsam\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? mband k\u233?nj\u250?t? N\u233?m\u233? \u225?mb yau! N\u233?m\u233? so y\u233?ndfem tawanang\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? mbandta? N\u233?m\u233? yau! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?yo, njam t\u233?fene y\u233?nmam njamke a s\u225?l\u225?me, y\u233?n\u233? fiya f\u233?yotaro t\u233?nmam t\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? efe m\u233?nde em wem\u225?rot ufogh yaman nuitat a nawametat ur\u233?ran t\u225?rf\u225?r mwighafnar a was\u233?rmbogh mwighayan, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam f\u225? ewewone wasneng\u233?ghfaf a was\u233?rmboghfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n mani uw\u233?gh siy\u233?m m\u233?inyotio yaufiyamoene s\u233?r\u233?mb. \u193?mb \u225?r y\u233?fenjo m\u233?ndeyan t\u233? n\u233?nguyangi, nayu namndangi ndimbal mwighata a y\u233?fene tik\u233?f kar\u233?fkar\u233?f nufrotat t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?uw\u233?ghofnar yaman.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Folene watamegh si Timotie
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?m, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r, takarota m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? yam. N\u225?sm\u233?ta m\u233?n\u225?t mbark\u225?nd gh\u233?rsat, ng\u225?nj\u225?n gh\u225?rsat, ndimbal mwigh\u233?, uw\u233?gh, m\u233?tar, a meraf\u233? yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Mer w\u233?rse yafrota fendio ndimbal mwigham\u233?n, a nawereta tuot gh\u233?rsat fendio; m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rsat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam n\u233?motai f\u233?m njam taikrataye norayam fenjo ndimbal mwigham\u233?n t\u225?rf\u225?r gh\u233?k\u233?f fandagh \u225?r s\u225?fr\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene gh\u233?kfan, emo ewaramete gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233?inyotio rokarat, a Keriso Yesue gh\u233?kfan, emo taikrataye norayam y\u225?ne ndimbal mwigham\u233?n Fontius Failetene gh\u233?kfan, y\u233?ndon n\u233?mafaretan f\u233?m muyaye {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t k\u225?y\u225?re fenjo w\u225?faregh a ew\u233?reta ndimbal mwighaye k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?n\u233? efogh njam t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Keriso kufarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u225?ne ufar\u233?gh siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mbark\u225?nd kw\u233?fon. Ng\u225?nj\u225?n siy\u233?m freng\u233?ghkaf a m\u233? f\u225?ro Lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r, warsagh \u225?rfene Warsagh \u225?r, a yurafene Yur\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u225?ro y\u233?m k\u233?rofnar; f\u225? y\u233?mor kwayagh\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n nden\u233? efe yau so kaflang\u233? kaka. Emon yau yinjoi f\u225?; emon yau so tinjong\u233? f\u225?. M\u233? y\u225?faf\u233?tro utman\u233?gh a tuot waft\u233?! Efalo.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Ewafareta f\u225? efe wem\u225?r em y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan yau so tuktukan em, w\u233?nde t\u225?kmangi y\u233?fene m\u233?ghm\u233?gh, yau nden\u233? wem\u225?r rokaran, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n k\u233?nj\u250?nro, emo marataye y\u233?nmaramete t\u233?fe m\u233?inyotio rokar t\u233?fene \u225?uw\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Ewafareta f\u225? meryam wafrogh\u233?t, wem\u225?r aem mer \u225?s\u225?foghan, marataye \u225?r aem a afreng\u233?ghkaf \u225?mb \u225?r w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? ende y\u233?mofem so ewamndat y\u233?fendio ngonj\u233?l \u225?rk\u233? so y\u233?m sotaf\u233? t\u233?f\u233?n soram\u233? yutau. A f\u233?yo y\u233?mofem so tanangi gh\u233?rs\u233? \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m efalo gh\u233?rs\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Timoti, ewarawena n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? eraman fene ng\u225?ngat. Nawarawena fifiofnar a mwighafnar amror\u233?ghta n\u233?m\u233? uny\u233?ghe \u225?mb \u225?r norayat nden\u233?, "Matyam" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r norayat t\u233? yanang\u233?m, w\u233?nde y\u233?nayoene fifi y\u233?mofem t\u233? t\u233?l\u225?itat ndimbal mwighane end.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?m so y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf m\u233?inyotio.
