Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Fol, Keriso Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?ndeyan w\u233?nmafaretam uny\u233?ghofnar gh\u233?rs\u233? si afrogh\u233?t \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m Keriso Yesue k\u233?nj\u250?n,
