K\u233?t\u225?n Timoti, tane tikfaf\u233? ambum:
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Af\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a Keriso Yesu t\u233?fene Yuram so k\u233?maramang\u233? ng\u225?r\u225?m, gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233?, a krufr\u225?t.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 K\u225?njo ram\u233?gh a waw\u233?ngsogh yam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?ndon k\u225?njo y\u233?rametan Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne, endeyot y\u233?nd efalo n\u225?s\u225?fotan, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? tane \u225?kif k\u233?s tamorw\u233?n. Y\u233?ndon k\u225?njo yarametan nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndon k\u233?s n\u233?mafarotan f\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n tane Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n s\u233?mb\u225?r a efogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?mawafarotan fene yengam, a y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m fe fandagh\u233?t mindefifi, m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? y\u233?nd so \u225?uw\u233?gham kwafong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?mawafarotan fene ndimbal mwigh\u233?, y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?fot ndimbal mwigh\u233? nden\u233? fenjo al\u233? Lois a fenjo am\u233? Yunis nden\u225?yo tawarw\u233?n. Y\u233?nd nden\u233? nemnan fene nden\u233?yameyo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
