s\u233?n ram\u233?gh, mwighafnar yam wafrogh, minde tuktukan, uw\u233?gh so y\u233?m fifi m\u233?ndeyan minde w\u233?nde yau uw\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
so em ng\u225?nj\u225?n gh\u233?rsaf\u233? \u225?rnit, w\u233?nde y\u233?kenat y\u225?ne efalo waft\u233?. Nayu aem y\u233?fe tamb\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r eng\u233?m \u225?rfene m\u233?ngot a \u225?fr\u225?t tinjongi njang\u233?n amafefaf efe etumndat y\u233?fenjo yaufiyamam a englimndat f\u233?natayo yaufi mwigham, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
y\u233?n\u233? amafam efe y\u233?ta t\u250?m\u233?n nawatametat tot\u233?r yam, w\u233?nde yaufifi so tanangi efalo matyamm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Janes a Jambres as\u233?nan\u233?gh \u225?r tarw\u233?n Mosesefaf, w\u233?i y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r\u233?m t\u233?karotaw\u233?t efalo si. Y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? yau n\u225?s\u225?fotat mere a efe uy\u233?gh \u225?r ere ndimbal mwighayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? yau so eyow\u233? matyaman nayu, m\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m so efandat nder\u233? onon f\u225? ere. Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? n\u233?m\u233? kufrotau y\u233?fefaf Janes a Jambres.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Kerkerm\u233?n watamegh
