W\u233?nde f\u233?mon t\u233? t\u233?rse tane watamegh, tane wafroghyam, a tane yam gh\u233?rs\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n; f\u233?mon t\u233? taf\u233?nmete tane ndimbal mwigh\u233?, tane m\u233?tar yam, tane uw\u233?gh, tane awamarogh, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
tane t\u225?rf\u225?r was\u233?rmboghyam, a tane t\u233?kratyam. F\u233?m mat n\u233?m m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? kufrotaw\u233?t tafaf Antiok, Ikonium a Listran, ndimbal t\u233?kratfifi y\u233?ndo y\u233?rsam\u233?n! W\u233?nde Yuram wanjary\u233?ng y\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? m\u233?inyotio y\u233?feta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
M\u233?inyotio \u225?r efe m\u233?nde em m\u233?n\u225?t ng\u225?nj\u225?n gh\u233?rs\u233? Keriso Yesu k\u233?nj\u250?n so em was\u233?rmboghyaman; {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
a yaufi \u225?r a uny\u233?gh \u225?r so yaufi n\u225?y\u225?totat k\u233?t\u225?n minde yaufi. \u193?mb \u225?r so ewawindat a w\u233?i f\u225?yo so nawawindat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde nden\u233? f\u233?m, m\u233?nj miya n\u233?ng\u233?rnyang efalo sian nden\u233? f\u233?m k\u233?s k\u233?nmatametan a taikrataye efalo tiy\u225?to. F\u233?m mat n\u233?m efe fene watamegh \u225?r tamorw\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
a f\u233?m kawafarota nden\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndmayo f\u233?m k\u233?nmorw\u233?n tos\u233?, f\u233?m mat t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?toi nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar Buk si, \u225?rk\u233? m\u233?n\u225?yam so n\u233?maramete fe k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yam so n\u233?limnde k\u233?t\u225?n wanjargh\u233?t ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? Keriso Yesu k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
M\u233?inyotio Buk si siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? y\u233?tetay\u233?ng fifiotyo m\u233?n\u225?t efalo si watamegh\u233?t, witr\u233?mbogh\u233?t m\u225?m\u225?fi, yaufi freng\u233?gh\u233?t, watamegh m\u233?n\u225?t mbark\u225?nd \u225?mnjogh\u233?t, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe n\u225?s\u225?fote Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne so y\u233?m mer freng\u233?gh \u225?r a watameghkaf m\u233?inyotio f\u233?natayero meryam wafrogh\u233?t.
