\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene s\u225?fr\u233?re a Keriso Yesuene s\u225?fr\u233?re, emo so mogh yafrote gh\u233?rs\u233? \u225?rfaf a k\u233?r \u225?rfaf, a m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? n\u233?nangote m\u233?n\u225?t lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Warsagh \u225?r, y\u233?ndon sotaf\u233? n\u233?maw\u233?ngsotan f\u233?m: {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si y\u233?ngwaitota. Afreng\u233?ghkaf so n\u233?m t\u225?f njam mer kw\u233?f y\u233?m o yau. M\u233?tare ewenda, taikrataye emndeta, a ewaw\u233?ngsota fene \u225?r mer watameghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Efogh y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m njam \u225?r yau so n\u225?y\u225?retat mbark\u225?nd sifaf, w\u233?nde so ewaitotat y\u233?fenjo m\u233?ndero a so ekafetat y\u233?fendio t\u225?rf\u225?r watamegh \u225?r efe so nafrotat y\u233?feyot n\u233?mat f\u225? m\u233?nde em \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u225? so kawengongi k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? efalo si \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghta a taramangi y\u233?fene t\u233?ngan k\u233?t\u225?n niny\u233? sifaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?m so nawarawene f\u233?myo m\u233?inyotio yamam\u233?, amyogh k\u233?rtayan, yafrota \u225?s\u225?fogh nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? mer sioene waitogh \u225?r, a yafrota fenjo \u225?s\u225?fogh nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Nden\u233? tayot siy\u233?m, kw\u233?f t\u233? nawer ta m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i karaman. Kw\u233?f siy\u233?m y\u233?na y\u233?m ta m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? orogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?nd t\u233? k\u225?smetan mer \u225?sm\u233?gh. Y\u233?ndon t\u233? yifon tane w\u233?rse. Y\u233?ndon t\u233? tamndan ndimbal mwigh\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
A s\u233?nonjo k\u233?t\u233? siy\u233?m ta nawanjete mbark\u225?nd fai, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? Yur\u233?, mbark\u225?nd Mogh \u225?rom, so kwaramang\u233? ta y\u233?n\u233? efghon a yau m\u233? tayotro, w\u233?nde m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t efe nawanjetat y\u225?ne ufargh\u233?t.
