Fenjo mer a yafrota m\u233?n\u225?t tafaf s\u225?i n\u233?n\u233?m w\u233?keye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Demas\u233?m t\u233? w\u233?frangoi y\u233?nd, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mo tauwetau y\u233?n\u233? mband marat rokar, y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan f\u225? nuwanoi Tesalonikat. Kresens t\u233? nuwanoi Galasia, a Taitus k\u233?t\u225?n Dalmasia. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Lukro siy\u233?m y\u233?na y\u233?m y\u233?ndf\u233?. T\u233?nmasro Mak a y\u233?n\u233?mnja f\u225? f\u233?mo, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mon so w\u225?ut\u225?ne ta \u225?s\u225?fogh k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?ndon y\u233?ngw\u225?f\u225?retan Tukikus Efesos\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Njam f\u233?m k\u233?nuwano, t\u233?nman tane s\u233?njt\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?ndon noroy\u233?n Karfusene m\u233?ngon Troas tesenan, a w\u233?i buk, nden\u225?yo \u225?mb w\u233?r\u225?r gh\u233?ngan wafroghm\u233?n.
