Aleksenda tot t\u233?f\u233?n \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r y\u233?nd y\u233?mon t\u225?rf\u225?r ende kwaghne. Yuram so taramang\u233? y\u225?ne fai nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mo t\u233? tafrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Aya kor anawarawena y\u225?nem\u233?n f\u233?myo, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mon t\u233?karotau mindefifi t\u233?fene si.
