Efe \u225?mb yau nokayoi ta kaka frondefifi kw\u233?fon y\u233?nd nawamarotay\u233?n y\u233?ndio. M\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m w\u233?frangoy\u233?nd. Y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? noraiwam nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n so tawalindang\u233? y\u233?fene yaufi! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
W\u233?nde Yuraf\u233? y\u233?nd t\u233?nmorare a waramay\u233?ng muy\u233?, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd so kw\u233?morw\u233?n si waitogh \u225?rro m\u233?inyotio T\u233?ndo \u225?r\u233?t \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t. A y\u233?nd kwanjarng\u233? k\u233?rta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
A Yuram so kwanjarng\u233? y\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? m\u233?inyotio yaufita a kwanang\u233? y\u233?nd y\u225?ne njafar lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t. M\u233? y\u225?faf\u233?tro ndimbal kwayagh\u233? y\u233?m tuot a tuot! Efalo.
