Erastus t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n Korint ndimbal yuwon, a y\u233?ndo y\u233?nfrangoy\u233?n Trofimus Miletus tesenan, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n enjne. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
