A y\u225?ne wafer\u233?gh efghon y\u233?mon safot y\u233?kmai y\u225?ne si k\u233?nj\u250?n. Y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?kmai tafaf, a y\u233?ndo t\u225?itotaw\u233?n nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233?fene Wanjar\u233?gh \u225?rom t\u233? norayai.
