Y\u233?ndon f\u233?m n\u233?frangoy\u233?n Kreten, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?mon so tifo t\u233?fene \u225?s\u225?fogh k\u233?t\u233? a takaf Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n s\u233?nko \u225?r m\u233?inyotio tesenam\u233?. Kawafarota tane wawanjagh: {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
s\u233?nko \u225?r ay\u233?m k\u233?rtafnar. Y\u225?ne so y\u233?m \u225?mbiro amaf, y\u225?ne ambum aem efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r a m\u233?inyotio mer gh\u233?rsaf\u233? a \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n s\u233?nko \u225?r y\u233?m gh\u233?k\u233?f fayogh \u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?s\u225?foghfaf, f\u225? t\u225?f y\u233?m k\u233?rtafnar. F\u225? yau y\u233?m f\u225?ro n\u225?s\u225?fota o tekofnar n\u233?kw \u225?r, o emo eneta w\u233?ri nu, o kw\u233?rnar \u225?r, o mani nit\u233? \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? ay\u233?m f\u250?tar wan t\u233?fn\u225?rfefaf, uw\u233?gh n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m mer, yandio awamarogh, mbark\u225?nd, nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar, awatamegh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u225? t\u225?f taikrataye nawereta efalo y\u225?togh sian y\u233?ndfem \u225?rk\u233? k\u233?n\u233?mndetam f\u233?m. Y\u233?n\u233? yameyo y\u233?mo so ewaw\u233?ngsote \u225?mb efalo watameghan a nden\u225?yo uyafogh y\u233?fene yaufi efe em akenagh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? t\u225?rf\u225?r em, efe em gh\u233?ngan n\u233?f\u233?gh \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n, efe \u225?y\u225?rghofnar em a \u225?mb \u225?r ewarsotat y\u233?fene fifiofnar yame. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u225? so k\u233?kmbongi, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mofem ewengotat m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?n efalota y\u233?fene uny\u233?gh watameghe, a m\u233?inyotio w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? yam mani wafrogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
\u193?mb Kretem\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r norayai, "Kretem\u233?n \u225?r t\u250?m\u233?n uny\u233?gh \u225?r, k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?r, a nit\u233? sak\u233?r ro." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? si efalo y\u233?m. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde ewarna f\u225? t\u233?krate, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? m\u233? so em ndimbal mwighayan {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
a yau y\u233?rsati Ju \u225?rfene niny\u233? si a \u225?rfene w\u225?faregh emofem y\u233?kenat efalo si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?feyot efe em nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar, m\u233?inyotio em nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar, w\u233?nde y\u233?feyot efe em was\u233?rmboghkaf a efalo y\u225?toghofnar, k\u233?t\u233? yau y\u233?m mer, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? a emar\u233?gh sem was\u233?rmboghkaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u225? norayat nden\u233? mat em Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem m\u233? y\u233?kenat y\u233?fenjoyo wafroghyaman. F\u225? em m\u233?ndm\u233?nd a \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar, f\u233?yotarofnar em mer wafrogh\u233?t.
