\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Mer wafrogh mer si t\u233?fnan
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?mo t\u225?f ewatameta ndern\u225?ye fifi y\u233?m sioene k\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Ewatameta bulu s\u225?i nawamarotat, mwigh\u233? taikre em, y\u233?fembia anawamarotat; mer aem y\u233?fene ndimbal mwighayan, uw\u233?ghan, a m\u233?taran. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Nden\u233? yameyo ewatameta aus\u233?aus\u233? s\u225?i emor nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar gh\u233?rsaye, yau t\u225?f em \u225?r si waruny\u233?gh \u225?r o yau t\u225?f em t\u225?rf\u225?r w\u233?ri nu n\u233?ne \u225?r. F\u225? t\u225?f ewatametat n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m mer. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? t\u225?f ewatametat tot\u233?r amafam s\u225?i euwetat y\u233?fenjo \u225?r a y\u233?fenjo ambum, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
so f\u225?yo nawamarotat a nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar em, a s\u225?i em mer m\u233?ngo amaf efe \u225?y\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?r em y\u233?fenjo \u225?rfefaf, m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si yau so y\u233?m utman\u233?ghofnar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Nden\u233? yameyo, ewaw\u233?ngsota tot\u233?r \u225?r s\u225?i em y\u233?fembia awamarogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
A f\u233?myo an\u233?m mer ufarogh m\u233?inyotio fene wafroghyame. A fene watamegh k\u233?nj\u250?n f\u233?m an\u233?m efaloe a t\u225?ik\u233?r mwighaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Noraya mbark\u225?nd siro m\u233?n\u225?t yau so n\u233?manangotat, m\u233?n\u225?t fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r so ekmete w\u225?iw\u225?iot a n\u233?m\u233? yaufi si yau so norayat t\u233?fenem\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r so f\u233?t\u233? em \u225?y\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?fenjo yurafefaf a remngogh \u225?r m\u233?inyotio yaman. Y\u233?mofem yau so ewawangotat y\u233?fenjo yurafet {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
o yau so oro nufrotat. W\u233?nde f\u225? t\u225?f nauyafotat nden\u233? f\u225? mer a efalo y\u225?togh k\u233?r ro em, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fene mer yamm\u233?n, m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m so yuyafotat ndimbal utman\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene watameghm\u233?n t\u233?fene Wanjar\u233?gh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? yuyafotam y\u225?njo ng\u225?r\u225?m m\u233?n\u225?t wanjar\u233?gh\u233?t m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?nayam y\u233?nmatamete y\u233?nd s\u225?i ekmbotam ng\u225?nj\u225?nofnar gh\u233?rs\u233? a mbandoene m\u233?nde, a s\u225?i y\u233?nmor y\u233?ndio awamaroghaf\u233?, mbark\u225?nd a ng\u225?nj\u225?n gh\u233?rsaye s\u233?nonjo efghon, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
njamandio y\u233?nd nawanjetam freng\u233?ghkaf efghot y\u233?nd m\u233?ghm\u233?gh \u225?ndan y\u233?n\u233?m, njam ndimbal kwayaghaf\u233? kufarng\u233? t\u233?fene ndimbal Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a Wanjar\u233?gh \u225?r, Yesu Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u225? t\u233? naramai f\u225?yo t\u233?feyot m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u233?nmanjarng\u233? k\u233?tam\u233? m\u233?inyotio yaufita a t\u233?ny\u225?tong\u233? nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar \u225?r efe em y\u225?ne kaf\u233?ghm\u233?n \u225?r a m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i ewafrotam mer.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Ewatameta y\u233?n\u233? yam a yafrota fenjo m\u233?inyotio muyaye m\u233?n\u225?t waw\u233?ngsogh\u233?t a mbark\u225?nd y\u225?togh\u233?t fenjo \u225?r. \u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau so n\u233?rete yuwot fefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 3
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Tafrota n\u233?m\u233? mer y\u233?m
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Mat ey\u225?tota fenjo \u225?r t\u225?f n\u225?myotat k\u233?t\u225?n gafaman lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?rfaf a muyaf\u233? \u225?r. Y\u233?mofem t\u225?f ewaitotat a afreng\u233?ghkaf aem m\u233?inyotio mer \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u225? yau t\u225?f yaufi si n\u233?ngamndetat, a aem krufr\u225?t a f\u250?tar awarny\u233?gh, a t\u250?m\u233?n meraf\u233? yam aem m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?nd y\u233?ndio t\u233?nmorw\u233?n fifiofnar, \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar a m\u225?m\u225?fi. Y\u233?nd t\u233?nmorw\u233?n faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r m\u233?inyotio f\u233?nat\u233? fifioene wayamnegh a m\u233?nde t\u225?rf\u225?ran. Y\u233?ndfem taramangay\u233?m t\u233?fene gh\u233?rs\u233? yaufifaf a waramnjagh, \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat t\u233?nfandaw\u233?t a y\u233?ndfem nden\u225?yo tafandaw\u233?m m\u233?ndm\u233?ndaf\u233? f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
W\u233?nde njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233?fene Wanjar\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m yuyafotam y\u225?njo meryam a uw\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?t, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
y\u233?mon y\u233?nd y\u233?nmanjary\u233?ng, yau m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?fenjoyo mbark\u225?nd yam wafroghm\u233?n, w\u233?nde m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?njo gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisaye. Y\u233?mon y\u233?nmanjary\u233?ng y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, emo y\u233?nmaramai t\u233?fe tot\u233?r \u225?r\u225?f\u233?gh a tot\u233?r gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233?naye umbarghe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yasury\u233?ng y\u225?njo Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r t\u233?fefaf marataye Yesu Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? t\u233?fene Wanjar\u233?gh \u225?r, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t y\u225?njo ng\u225?r\u225?me y\u233?nd mbark\u225?nd y\u233?ny\u225?toi Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? a y\u233?nmaramai m\u233?ghm\u233?gh tuot gh\u233?rsat \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m t\u233?fene sifay\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? si efalo y\u233?m. Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m f\u233?m s\u225?i ewatameta y\u233?n\u233? yamfaf, m\u233?n\u225?t emofem efalo yiy\u225?totat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n so mwigh\u233? y\u233?faronat meryam wafrogh\u233?t. Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m mer watamegh\u233?t a f\u233?yotaro m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde ekarotati mwighafnar \u233?wigh, \u225?kifene tomb\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?n s\u233?nagh, amror\u233?gh, \u225?sm\u233?gh n\u225?km\u233?n. Y\u233?n\u233? sem fifiofnar a k\u233?mbunofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Yaw\u233?ngsota s\u243?mbinotm\u233? emo y\u233?tiane afalogh, a y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, yau w\u233?ikor y\u233?f\u233?rta f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?m mat n\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r sem was\u233?rmbogh \u225?r, a y\u233?fene yaufiyamam ey\u225?tote nden\u233? yau em mer.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Njam y\u233?ndon t\u233?ngwatemban Atemas o Tukikus fefaf, mer yafrota m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?n\u233?m tafaf Nikofolis tesenot, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon t\u233? mwigh\u233? t\u233?faronan s\u225?i yunjfan w\u233?mor k\u233?t\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Tafrota fene mer w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t Njenas n\u225?k t\u233?fn\u225?rai a Afolos m\u233?n\u225?t k\u233?nufngend \u225?ligh a t\u233?nfandangend nden\u233? y\u233?fene t\u233? eware rokar f\u233?yotaro y\u233?fendio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
T\u233?fene \u225?r t\u225?f notametat m\u233?n\u225?t efogh s\u225?i ersat mer wafroghan, m\u233?n\u225?t so n\u233?us\u233?nat efalo m\u233?nde yamot, a f\u225? yau so emor fifiofnar.
