Tane Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh nden\u233? y\u233?m t\u233?fene f\u250?taryam f\u233?maf\u233? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r so y\u233?n\u233?rsam k\u233?njkam matyam m\u233?inyotio freng\u233?ghm\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? t\u233?fene em t\u233?fene gh\u233?rsayan Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Fene uw\u233?gham ta kwaramete ndimbal \u225?uw\u233?gh a waw\u233?ngsogh, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo, tane f\u250?tar\u233?m t\u233? ewafrenda m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?rfene tik\u233?f.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fol\u233?m y\u233?ng\u233?mndete Filemon y\u225?nem\u233?n Onesimus
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, ndemam\u233?n Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?nd yuwek w\u233?m siot a n\u233?mafaretan f\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t wafrogh\u233?t n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mo fiya tawafrotang. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?mon t\u250?m\u233?n euwete \u225?mb \u225?r, y\u233?ndon y\u233?n\u233? yafrotan, ndemam\u233?n y\u233?nd w\u233?m Fol, efe bulu y\u233?m a s\u233?nonjo w\u233?i w\u233?m kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngo \u225?r y\u225?ne Keriso Yesuene t\u233?fnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?nd nomnendan fefaf tane ambum Onesimus, efe n\u233?namndai tane ambum Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n, njamandio kw\u233?morw\u233?n kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon y\u233?ndon n\u233?namnday\u233?n y\u225?ne mb\u233?rmb\u233?re af\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Onesimus, efe fronde t\u233?morw\u233?n fifiofnar fefaf, w\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo fifiyaf\u233? y\u233?m feyot a tayot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?ndon s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ngwangotan f\u225? fefaf, efe y\u233?ng\u233?m tane tikfaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?nd y\u233?ta m\u233?nde kw\u233?m s\u225?i tangongay\u233?n f\u225? y\u233?na y\u233?ndf\u233?, njamandio y\u233?nd kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon w\u233?lau mer si t\u233?fnan, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mo so w\u225?ut\u225?ne ta fene sifayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd m\u233?ndefnar w\u233?m \u225?mb yam s\u225?i yafrotan fe matofnaye. Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde kw\u233?m f\u233?mo ta s\u225?i kw\u225?ut\u225?nau m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m m\u233?nde n\u233?m, yau m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u233?mafaretan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u225? t\u233? nafaloi fe tamb\u233?n yau tekot w\u233?nde f\u233?mo so tango fendio ambino, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
yau y\u233?m faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rro, w\u233?nde namndai minde tuk\u233?n a y\u225?inde faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? f\u250?tar. Y\u233?ndon yuwetan mindefifi. W\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo f\u233?mon so yuwete mindefifi. Y\u233?mon so fene \u225?s\u225?fogh yafrote nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, w\u233?nde y\u233?mon w\u233?i Yurane \u225?s\u225?fogh so yafrote nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?mon k\u233?s yafrote.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?mo njam y\u233?nd mwighaye w\u233?kwna nden\u233? f\u250?tar w\u233?m, tumyo t\u225?f f\u225? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?nd s\u225?i kumyo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Njam Onesimus\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? yaufi t\u233? yafrotam, y\u233?ndo so mbark\u225?nd tiy\u225?tong w\u233?ikor. Njam y\u233?mon t\u233? ewanai feta, y\u233?ndo so n\u233?mawafangotan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?ndo, Fol\u233?m so y\u233?farotan y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?n tanjo ng\u225?ngaye: Y\u233?ndon so fai k\u233?mawangong\u233?n. W\u233?nde f\u233?m so nawafarote y\u233?ndo n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? n\u233?maramay\u233?n fe. Fene gh\u233?rs\u233? siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon k\u233?maufrotan mer si Yesuenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?yo, tane f\u250?tar, tafrota tayot y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?nde Yurane t\u233?fnan, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u250?tar Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n, kw\u225?ut\u225?na y\u233?nd m\u233?n\u225?t kwiy\u225?to \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233?! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndon y\u233?farotan y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?n, y\u233?nd m\u233?inyo mat w\u233?m f\u233?mon so yafrote n\u233?mat y\u233?ndon n\u233?ngmamnendang\u233?n. Efalo y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? mer yam wafrogh f\u233?mon so yafrote y\u225?faf so taindang\u233? n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon n\u233?mndetan f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
\u193?mbiro yamro y\u233?m: t\u225?f y\u233?frenda \u225?mb m\u233?ngo tayot, m\u233?nam\u233?n tane m\u233?ghm\u233?gh nden\u233? nemnan y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so k\u225?y\u225?rang\u233? f\u233?fene oray\u233?gh m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd so ngwangong\u233? f\u233?fefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
\u193?uw\u233?gh si f\u233?feyot k\u233?tam\u233? Efafras, y\u233?ndf\u233? emaf\u233? y\u233?nyaweyay\u233?nd kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon Keriso Yesuene t\u233?fnan, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
