emofem t\u233? ernoy\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene sioene mer a waft\u233? soramam\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, y\u233?mofem euroy\u233?nd y\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?yotarofnar y\u233?m y\u233?fe wangogh\u233?t f\u225? w\u233?ikor yaufita awengogh\u233?t, m\u233?nam\u233?n w\u233?ikor y\u233?mofem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Ambum y\u233?namndat wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan a y\u233?kmetat w\u225?iw\u225?ian marataye.
