Mband \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam y\u233?nete nu afam\u233?ghm\u233?n t\u225?f njam nuite k\u233?t\u225?n a \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam efune mbwe fifiotio y\u233?feyot endefeyot eitam\u233?nd, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene freng\u233?gh y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde mband \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam y\u233?fune w\u233?tw\u233?t a yus t\u233?fnat, siy\u233?m fifiofnar. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tekofnar tafalngong\u233? y\u233?n\u233? mband. Soram\u233? so nak\u233?rne f\u233?s\u233?n.
