T\u233?fene tikfaf\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?ndfem ewaufrotam y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd m\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?m s\u225?i merero m\u233? eng\u233?m. Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? ewanjary\u233?ng f\u233?m a nden\u233? y\u233?mo so m\u233? eng\u233?frende f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u250?m\u233?n y\u233?m mbark\u225?nd. F\u225? yau so tawalindang\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh f\u233?mofem \u225?rk\u233? tawafrotati a uw\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? tuyafotati y\u225?yot y\u233?naye tarawenati \u225?mb efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r, nden\u233? f\u233?mofem m\u233? k\u233?s ewafrotati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
T\u233?fene ndimbal m\u233?nde siy\u233?m f\u233?mofem m\u233? so euwetati \u225?mb \u225?r y\u233?n\u233? teke njamandio gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233? em, m\u233?n\u225?t so nufrote nden\u233? n\u233?mat f\u233?m m\u233?ghm\u233?gh em so efalo tiy\u225?tongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?nd m\u233?ndefnar y\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?m s\u225?i k\u233?namndangi s\u225?k\u233?r, w\u233?nde s\u225?i ewaf\u233?nmetati f\u225? efe em ndimbal mwighaf\u233? a m\u233?tar gh\u233?rs\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? ewanay\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene uny\u233?ghofnar si.
