Njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam uny\u233?ghofnar si norayam Ebraamefaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? yau t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?mb ndimbalfifi Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u225?yot, y\u233?mo y\u225?njo y\u233?tkw\u233?nan norayai t\u225?f y\u233?mo njam yafrotam uny\u233?ghofnar si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u225? norayai, "Y\u233?ndo uny\u233?ghofnar si n\u233?mndetan f\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?ndon so k\u233?n\u233?frendang\u233?n f\u233?m, a k\u233?maraman t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?kiambum." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo Ebraam kawanjetau m\u233?tare, a y\u233?mo yanai n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si norayai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Njam \u225?r\u233?m uny\u233?ghofnar si ewafrotat, y\u233?mofem tanmongi \u225?mb \u225?r emo ewainde f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t so tawerang\u233? f\u225? k\u233?t\u233?. A uny\u233?ghofnar siam tafrendang\u233? m\u233?inyotio amror\u233?ghta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u225?i tuyafongai saf\u233?t nden\u233? y\u233?mo so tengongai y\u225?njo mwigh\u233?. F\u225? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u225?ne \u225?r mat so k\u225?y\u225?tongay\u233?nd nden\u233? y\u233?mo so tafrendangai f\u225?. F\u233?yo njam y\u233?mo uny\u233?ghofnar si yafrotam, y\u233?mo w\u233?i y\u225?njo y\u233?tkw\u233?nan norayai m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u225?ik\u233?r tiy\u225?tongai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? y\u233?nmaramai t\u233?fe y\u233?n\u233? s\u243?mbio yam, y\u225?ne uny\u233?ghofnar si a sotaf\u233? si. Y\u233?n\u233? s\u243?mbio yam sere wengoghofnar m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m f\u233?yotarofnar y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n s\u225?i nuinda. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, y\u233?nd efe t\u233? nenngoy\u233?m y\u225?faf m\u233?n\u225?t wanjargh\u233?t so y\u233?m t\u225?ik\u233?r mwigh\u233? s\u225?i y\u233?ndfem y\u233?retam m\u233?ghm\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? y\u233?ramai t\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
T\u233?fene y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ghm\u233?gh nden\u233? bout k\u233?mboghm\u233?n tot t\u233?f\u233?nnit t\u233?fene gh\u233?rsat. Y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m t\u225?ik\u233?r a awafarogh\u233?t, a y\u233?ng\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar satat w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngot ndimbal s\u225?l\u225?me \u225?rk\u233? tamang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
M\u233?n\u225?t t\u233?fe w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t, Yesu fronde n\u233?lawai y\u233?n\u233? satat. F\u225? t\u233? n\u233?namndai lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r tuot, nden\u233? Melkisedek.
