Njam gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh yam tengongai, n\u225?k w\u233?i nden\u225?yo so tawengongai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u225?nem\u233?n y\u233?nd snorayam y\u233?m f\u233?nataye m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n, endefene \u225?r yau n\u225?s\u225?fotat gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitarayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?s\u233?rmbnan siy\u233?m, t\u233?fene Yur\u233? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? Judane m\u233?r\u233?nta, a Moses\u233?m yau emndai Judane m\u233?r\u233?n s\u225?i kufnyangay\u233?nd gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?s\u225?foghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?nd t\u233? korayam t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?tote saf\u233?nro s\u233?nonjo. \u193?mb s\u225?fot gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r t\u233? nufar, efe y\u233?m gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r ndenanit Melkisedek. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
