W\u233?nde, f\u225? k\u225?ronjaw\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t merfifi yuwot, njafar m\u233?ngotuot. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n w\u233?i yau w\u225?iw\u225?i y\u233?m s\u225?i y\u233?mndetat y\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mo t\u233? y\u233?frendam ndimbal tesen y\u233?feyot.
