Ndemam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?mndai f\u225?, "Aiseke k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? fene m\u233?r\u233?n so n\u233?ngusamngote." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
