Ndimbal mwighaye Moses y\u225?refafem y\u225?tmaf\u233? y\u233?tneyay\u233?nd nambio gh\u233?rare y\u225?njoyo m\u233?rnam njam f\u225? n\u225?r\u225?ftam. Y\u233?mofem yinjeyay\u233?nd f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n mer ambum, a f\u225? yau tarw\u233?n f\u233?rf\u233?r warsagh \u225?roene wafroghyamm\u233?n.
