Emofem ndimbal mwighaye t\u233?tumndangay\u233?nd warsagh \u225?rfene yu, a tawafrotaw\u233?t wafroghyam mbark\u225?ndero, a tawanangay\u233?nd n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam uny\u233?ghofnar si norayai, emofem tamnangay\u233?nd ndimbal munjan fusafene s\u233?nfne, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
tang\u233?umb\u233?rtotaw\u233?t f\u233?s k\u225?nk\u233?k\u225?nk\u233?, a kunjarngay\u233?nd k\u233?rta k\u233?tam\u233? witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?ifata. Y\u233?fene muyafnar fifi stamorw\u233?n kaw\u233?ngongay\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n muyat. F\u225? k\u233?namndangay\u233?nd muyaf\u233? m\u233?kan a t\u225?kmangay\u233?nd y\u233?fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r wifargh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
