F\u233?m yau mat em n\u233?m\u233? so katyarng\u233? k\u225?ye. F\u233?fene gh\u233?rs\u233? em esnit \u225?rk\u233? kufarngi m\u233? tekofnar a ngolindangi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde, f\u233?m nden\u233? f\u225?i korayangi, "Njam y\u233?m Yurane m\u233?nde, y\u233?nd so y\u233?nmor a yafrotam y\u233?n\u233? o \u225?mb k\u233?s." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Nden\u233? siy\u233?m, f\u233?m nawarmbotati a tuktuk si norayati, m\u233?inyotio tuktuk siy\u233?m yaufi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, y\u233?ndfem yau njam ewafrotam mer y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?ndfem s\u225?i tawafrotang\u233?m, y\u233?ndfem yaufiyam t\u233?f\u233? yafrotam.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 5
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Waw\u233?ngsogh k\u233?t\u225?n wem\u225?r \u225?r\u233?t
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
F\u233?m wem\u225?r \u225?r, k\u225?y\u225?rangi tafaf. Ye nendati a nawarametati m\u233?nam\u233?n wasneng\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u233?fene wem\u225?r rokar norndat a gh\u233?njam enetat f\u233?fene s\u225?l\u225?me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?fene gol a silf\u233? em nek\u233?rnek\u233?raf\u233? a y\u233?fene nek\u233?rnek\u233?r so em afrogh\u233?t f\u233?fenem\u233?n a so enetat f\u233?fene fifi ndenanit f\u233?s. F\u233?mofem tumendati rokar kerker efghon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?mofem yau \u225?mb fai tawafrotati y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe k\u225?s\u225?fotat f\u233?fene ndawan. K\u225?y\u225?rangi! F\u233?mofem t\u233? tawasotati f\u225? a s\u233?nonjo f\u225? nawatarnat f\u233?fefaf. Ndimbal Waftaf\u233? Yuram t\u233? ey\u225?r\u233? f\u225? njam f\u225? kutnat y\u225?faf m\u233?n\u225?t w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t. F\u225? mat y\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?m sem k\u233?rtaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?m t\u233? tamor y\u233?na mband maratan kawayotati mer rokare. F\u233?m t\u233? k\u233?minati y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fot ngifaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?mofem t\u233? takmetati k\u233?rtayan a t\u225?smetati krot m\u233?nd \u225?r, emofem yau k\u233?nkarotaw\u233?t f\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 M\u233?tar t\u233?krat k\u233?nj\u250?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u250?tar\u233?f, aem m\u233?tar k\u233?t\u225?notio Yurane angogh. Y\u233?fandati ndern\u225?ye ndau t\u233?fn\u225?r nawanjete mbandfaf s\u225?i efuna merfifi njamke t\u233?f\u233?n, a nder\u233? m\u233?tare nawanjete k\u233?t\u225?n uf\u233?rtogh a kianj nufaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?m w\u233?i t\u225?f aem m\u233?tar a ewakai taikre, m\u233?nam\u233?n Yurane angogh siy\u233?m kaka. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u250?tar\u233?f, yau nawatarnati f\u233?mro f\u233?mro o f\u233?m so em moghan. Mogh t\u233?fn\u225?r yakai kaka s\u233?safnefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u250?tar\u233?f, nawafarotati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r efe korayaw\u233?t Yurane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan. F\u233?mofem t\u250?m\u233?n so ewaitotati y\u233?fene yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?m mat em y\u233?ndfem efalo ey\u225?totam f\u225? em freng\u233?gh efe t\u233? kawamarotaw\u233?t. F\u233?m t\u233? k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t Jobene awamaroghm\u233?n, a t\u233? yinjoi n\u233?m\u233? Yuram t\u233? y\u233?nmarsam k\u233?t\u225?n kerkerfaf. Yur\u233? y\u233?m minde mer a gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? afoghare.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? tuk\u233?n m\u233?inyotio, tane f\u250?tar, yau t\u225?f olaghofnar si norayati njafare o mband maratoe o \u225?mb rokare. M\u233?inyotio f\u233?fene siot s\u225?i ewam nekambe "O" o "Yau, " a f\u233?yo f\u233?m yau so en\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mogh mbanmbanan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
T\u233? f\u233?m \u225?mb em k\u233?rtayan? F\u225? so Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayat. T\u233? \u225?mb em \u225?uw\u233?ghan? Y\u233?mofem so eufanat wagh \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
T\u233? \u225?mb em enjnef\u233?? Y\u233?mofem so tamotangi Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n s\u233?nko \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf oraigh\u233?t y\u233?feyot a efaghanat oile Yurane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
A Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh wategh ndimbal mwighayan so tay\u225?tong\u233? enjnef\u233? \u225?r mer a Yuram so tafrendang\u233?. Njam y\u233?mofem t\u233? tafrotat yaufiyam, y\u233?fene so tawawayang\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde eufanati f\u233?fenjo yaufiyam f\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n a Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati f\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so mer k\u225?y\u225?tongi. Mbark\u225?nd \u225?roene Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh siy\u233?m waft\u233? k\u233?r ro a f\u233?yotaro y\u233?m \u225?mb \u225?r w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Elaija t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?r nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?nd. F\u225? Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiw\u233?t tikfe nden\u233? yau so nu kafamndau, a yau nafamndam mbandan nambio a mbarmbar yunj\u233?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
W\u233?ikor f\u225? Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiw\u233?t, a njafaram y\u233?ramay\u233?ng nu, a mbandam wanogh y\u233?ngwafngoi njamke t\u233?f\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, t\u225?f \u225?mb f\u233?m njam n\u233?w\u233?rsota k\u233?tam\u233? efalota a \u225?mb \u225?rom so f\u233?t\u233? f\u225? t\u233?nmangong\u233? w\u233?ikor, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
nawafarotati y\u233?n\u233?: Emo njam tengong\u233? yaufiyam t\u233?fn\u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? mbark\u225?ndofnaye yamta so tanjarng\u233? f\u225? k\u233?tam\u233? k\u233?rta a tawalindang\u233? t\u225?rf\u225?r yaufiyam.
