Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Fit\u233?, Yesu Kerisoene muyaf\u233? \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?ndo y\u233?farotan k\u233?t\u225?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene wafer\u233?ghm\u233?n \u225?r, wan t\u233?fn\u225?r mband maratan nofarnam\u233?nd y\u233?nam\u233? Fontus, Galasia, Kafadokia, Esia a Bitinia. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Af\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n mat t\u233?morw\u233?n a ekafai frondeyo, a Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram t\u233? ey\u225?toi f\u233?m nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar. F\u233?yo f\u233?mofem t\u233? yiy\u225?retati Yesu Keriso a y\u225?n\u233? f\u233?rkam eumbary\u233?ng f\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ng\u225?r\u225?m a krufr\u225?t so y\u233?m f\u233?fene m\u233?inyoe.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 \u193?uw\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?neyot gh\u233?rsam\u233?n m\u233?ghm\u233?gh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
\u193?uw\u233?gh k\u233?t\u225?n Af\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne a t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Keriso! Y\u225?njo ndimbal gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisaye y\u233?mo t\u233? y\u233?nmaramai t\u233?fe tot\u233?r \u225?r\u225?f\u233?gh k\u233?t\u225?n gh\u233?rsam\u233?n m\u233?ghm\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n Yesu Kerisoene anogh k\u233?tam\u233? k\u233?rta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?nd nawanjetam s\u225?i tawanang\u233?m m\u233?inyotio mer rokar Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? tafrende t\u233?feyot. \u193?rk\u233? \u225?r\u233?m yau so ewaghne o ewas\u233?rmbote or yau so k\u233?rk\u233?f kamndangi. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewamnde y\u233?n\u233? rokar njafaran f\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
A ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewanjane y\u225?ne waftaye k\u233?t\u225?notio f\u233?mofem so tanangi y\u233?n\u233? wanjar\u233?gh, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m freng\u233?ghkaf s\u225?i nufrota kerker efghon.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
M\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m ndimbale n\u225?uw\u233?tati, ndemam\u233?n s\u233?nonjo tekofnarot \u225?uw\u233?ghofnar em m\u233?inyotio f\u233?nat\u233? ufoghyamam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?fene fifi siy\u233?m yiy\u225?tote nden\u233? f\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233? so em mer. Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? gol yufotam\u233?nd f\u233?san, f\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233?, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam y\u225?inde gol, so y\u233?m ufoghan, m\u233?n\u225?t so nawamarotati. F\u233?mofem so tawanangi \u225?uw\u233?gh a ndimbal kwayagh\u233? a utman\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233? efghon njam Yesu Keriso kufarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?mofem yau yinjoy\u233?nd Yesu, w\u233?nde m\u233? yuwetati f\u225?, a f\u233?mofem yau y\u233?fandati Yesu s\u233?nonjo, w\u233?nde efalo yiy\u225?totati f\u225?. F\u233?yo f\u233?m so n\u225?uw\u233?tati ndimbale a ndimbal kwayaghaf\u233? \u225?uw\u233?ghe \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? siam yau so yafenat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem tanangi wanjar\u233?gh, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m fai f\u233?fene ndimbal mwigham\u233?n y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? wanjar\u233?ghm\u233?n, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?m t\u233?ronjaw\u233?t merk\u233?r\u225?ye a ndimbal warawer\u233?ghaf\u233?, a kafrotaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? ng\u225?r\u225?mm\u233?n \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tawaramangai f\u233?fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?ta t\u233?ronjaw\u233?t endefaf Kerisoene Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n t\u233? tawauyafotau a \u225?rk\u233? efoghm\u233?n f\u225? korayau, njam f\u225? korayau fronde nden\u233? Kerisom so yamarote t\u233?krat a ndimbal kwayagh\u233? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam so yaitote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam tuyafotau y\u225?ne Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?t nden\u233? y\u225?njo si y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n t\u233?morw\u233?n yau efalo y\u233?fe w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t w\u233?nde f\u233?fe w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t. W\u233?nde, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmafaretam y\u225?njo si y\u233?fe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?t f\u233?fe w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t. Y\u233?n\u233? si siy\u233?m mer si Yesu Kerisoenem\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m f\u233?mofem s\u233?nonjo t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?retati. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmafaretam Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r njafarta \u225?r w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i ewaufroy\u233?nd mer si f\u233?fe. Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m minde merfifi y\u233?m nden\u233? njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r so m\u233?nde tamorw\u233?n matot.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Aem nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, f\u233?fene mwigh\u233? tafrendangi \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t. Kor aem a t\u225?kmangi f\u233?fene m\u233?ghm\u233?gh m\u233?inyoe freng\u233?ghfaf \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tawaramang\u233? f\u233?fe njam Yesu Keriso kufarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Aem \u225?y\u225?r\u233?gh k\u233?r ro Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf, a yau eumyotati f\u233?fenjo gh\u233?rs\u233? s\u225?i efanat y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ndeyam njam f\u233?m m\u233? tamorw\u233?n \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde, nden\u233? f\u225? emo emotai f\u233?m siy\u233?m nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar, y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n aem nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar m\u233?inyotio yam wafrogh k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
