Njam y\u233?mon t\u233? t\u233?kratan ekmeyai ndimbal tesen Sodom a Gomora m\u233?n\u225?yan ewak\u233?rnam k\u233?t\u225?n mbangmbang, a yafrotam y\u233?fefaf ufarogh n\u233?m\u233? so n\u233?ngufrote ng\u225?nj\u225?nofnar \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
A njam t\u233? y\u233?mo yanjary\u233?ng Lot, mbark\u225?nd \u225?r, ende t\u233?krat tarametaw\u233?t yaufi wal yame n\u225?kofnar \u225?r\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? mbark\u225?nd \u225?r t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n, t\u250?m\u233?n efogh y\u233?mon t\u233?fandau nd\u233?mke njam tafandau a k\u225?y\u225?retau y\u233?fene yaufi wafroghyamm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m efalo, y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n Yur\u233? mat y\u233?m ndern\u225?ye so ewanjane ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? ufogh yamta a s\u225?i ewereta mbark\u225?ndofnar \u225?r moghfaf y\u233?n\u233? mogh efghon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u225? efe eyota fifioene m\u233?ndeyan yaghnat a y\u233?kenat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene waft\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?n\u233? uny\u233?gh watamegh \u225?r f\u233?rf\u233?rofnar a tuktukan em, a yau yuyafotat utman\u233?gh k\u233?t\u225?n ndimbal kwayaghaf\u233? \u225?rfefaf; w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem ewasalitat f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r\u233?m ewaindat y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r a em minde tuk\u233?n a waftaf\u233?, y\u233?mofem yau tamndetaw\u233?t yaufi si Yurane s\u225?fr\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? uny\u233?gh watamegh \u225?r sem ndenanit k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t wergh\u233?t a krot. F\u225? n\u233?nwangotat t\u233?krate f\u225? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? mafina em. F\u225? so kolindangi ndenanit k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u225? so fai ewafrotat t\u233?krate y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?krateyo y\u233?mofem \u225?rk\u233? tafrotat. M\u233?nde y\u233?fene siy\u233?m s\u225?i ewafrotat saf\u233?n efogh kwayaghayan \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam so eremngote y\u233?fene fifi amanjarghan. F\u225? em w\u225?iw\u225?i a ng\u225?r\u225?mofnar nden\u233? k\u233?s nufeindat f\u233?fene njamkeyan, m\u233?inyotio yaman n\u225?uwetat y\u233?fene yaufiyamm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Wal gh\u233?k\u233?f amafanyo, f\u225? yau k\u233?kmbongi yaufiyam. Y\u233?mofem engwaramnat yau k\u233?kmbongi. F\u225? em nit\u233?. F\u225? sem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene wafalngogh mbanmbanan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?mofem t\u233? norongi mbark\u225?nd end a mwigh\u233? yaitongi s\u225?i yaitotat Bejerene ambum Balamene yam, emo m\u233?ndef\u233? tafandau yaufiyam wafrogh\u233?t mani faie. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? yus\u233?rmbotam siofnar ndonkiam m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?njoyo yaufiyamm\u233?n, korayau \u225?r si k\u233?me a y\u233?kmbotam y\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfene m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye yam.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r sem ndenanit sotro nu y\u233?kwnit a esnit \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?ngtarne m\u233?n\u225?yam mbormboram. Minde kw\u233?fit\u233? nawanjete y\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u225? nawarmbotat a fifiofnar sie ewafrotat, a yaufi wal m\u233?ndeye ereindat f\u225? emofem y\u233?rnyangi k\u233?tam\u233? nawanjarngi \u225?r efe emorm\u233?n yaufi gh\u233?rsaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?mofem uny\u233?ghofnar si ewaramay\u233?nd y\u233?fe yuwekm\u233?n, t\u225?f f\u225? f\u225?yo em faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r was\u233?rmboghan m\u233?nam\u233?n, "\u225?r ey\u225?tote faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r n\u233?m\u233? yam t\u233? elimnde f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? uny\u233?gh watamegh \u225?r mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd y\u225?nem\u233?n t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Keriso, emo y\u233?nmanjane y\u233?nd. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, f\u225? t\u233? n\u233?kmboy\u233?nd yaufi wafroghta \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? em mband maratoene. F\u225? t\u233? n\u233?namnday\u233?nd yuwek k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yam waftata. W\u233?nde soram\u233? njam y\u233?mofem w\u233?i ewafrotat y\u233?n\u233? yaufi yamyo, f\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? yam wafrogh so k\u233?namndangi minde muyaf\u233? a taumbangi y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r w\u233?ikor a f\u225? so awas\u233?rmboghan em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Nden\u233? \u225?r\u233?m yau fia tinjongay\u233?nd mbark\u225?nd end. Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n tekofnar emorm\u233?n a nangoy\u233?nd. Njam nangoy\u233?nd ekenay\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene minde muyaf\u233? si y\u233?mon \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? ewaramai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
A s\u243?mbio k\u225?fet\u233? si efalo nufrotam y\u233?fefaf. \u193?mb si noraye, "\u193?gh\u233? m\u233?nd nawetotam a y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n a soram\u233? n\u233?nangotam a enete w\u233?ikor y\u225?njo m\u233?nd." A \u225?mb si noraye, "Kimb kumbnau mer nuan a n\u233?wanoi a w\u233?i n\u233?nangoi a k\u225?y\u225?totau gh\u233?ndan."
