\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
\u193?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m s\u233?nonjo y\u233?namayo f\u233?r\u233?n f\u233?fefaf. Y\u233?ndon t\u233? efarom\u233?n s\u243?mbio f\u233?r\u233?n f\u233?fefaf mwighat minagh\u233?t f\u233?fe \u225?mbiro mwighayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m f\u233?m s\u225?i nawafarotati si n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? k\u233?norayaw\u233?t t\u225?nd\u225?i y\u233?mofem nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r a w\u225?faregh si y\u233?nmaramay\u233?ng t\u233?fene Yuram a Wanjar\u233?gh \u225?rom f\u233?fene Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Frondefifi, f\u233?m a mat n\u225?y\u225?totati nden\u233? k\u233?t\u233? kerker efghon si wafrogh \u225?r so en\u233?m, si so engwafrotat a ewaitotat y\u233?fenjo yaufiyam m\u233?nde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u225? so norayat, "\u193?nde y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? 'angogh' y\u233?mo sy\u233?ngufoi? K\u233?t\u225?ndmayo t\u233?fene \u225?kif t\u233? k\u233?r enmorm\u233?n, m\u233?inyotio m\u233? n\u233?ngrete nden\u233? endeyo k\u233?t\u225?ndmayo mband marat fronde n\u233?nufrotam." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? fifiyanyo ewawalinde nden\u233? t\u225?nd\u225?i y\u233?naye Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene sie njafar naketat a mband marat yafrotam k\u233?tam\u233? nuta a m\u233? nuero. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? nue w\u233?i mband marat y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?kmang\u233?rm\u233?n k\u233?f\u233?r a y\u233?rambary\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? sieyo s\u233?nonjo njafar a mband marat nawamndat k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?s\u233?t, em k\u233?t\u225?n mogh efogh a t\u233?krat yam ng\u225?nj\u225?nofnar \u225?rfet.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, w\u233?nde yau tawawalindang\u233? y\u233?n\u233? \u225?mbiro yam: Yurafaf \u225?mbiro efogh siy\u233?m ndenanit 1,000 yunj\u233?f, a 1,000 yunj\u233?f ndenanit \u225?mbiro efogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Yur\u233? yau y\u233?m awan\u233?ghe s\u225?i nufrota y\u225?ne uny\u233?ghofnar si, nden\u233? \u225?mb n\u233?ngemnat so nawanete. W\u233?nde f\u225? siy\u233?m m\u233?tar f\u233?maf\u233?, yau m\u233?nde y\u233?m \u225?mb \u225?r s\u225?i kolindang\u233?, w\u233?nde m\u233?inyotio \u225?r s\u225?i kawengongi yaufiyamta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
W\u233?nde Yurane efogh so y\u233?n\u233?m ndenanit oro t\u233?fn\u225?r. Njafar so nolindat ukef\u233?. F\u233?sam so yas\u233?rmbote m\u233?inyotio rokar. Mband marat a m\u233?inyotio rokar n\u233?m\u233? \u225?r\u233?m ewafrotat so kolindangi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so ewas\u233?rmbote m\u233?inyotio rokar y\u233?n\u233? ende, f\u233?m efalo mat em ndernaye f\u233?mofem t\u225?f so n\u225?s\u225?fotati. F\u233?m so emor nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar a ng\u225?nj\u225?n gh\u233?rsaye {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
njamandio f\u233?m n\u233?retati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene efghot a w\u233?keye tiy\u225?tongi y\u225?ne \u225?ligh. Y\u233?n\u233? efgham so y\u233?n\u233?rs\u233? t\u233?krat yam njafar s\u225?i em f\u233?san, a m\u233?inyotio rokar so n\u233?rndat waftam\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde yeretam y\u225?ne uny\u233?ghofnar si y\u233?nd n\u233?retam k\u233?t\u225?n tot\u233?r njafar a tot\u233?r mband marat, \u225?nde mbark\u225?nd yam so n\u225?s\u225?fotat.
