Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?m n\u233?retati k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?nat m\u233?inyotio yamm\u233?n a tawinjong\u233? mborofnar, t\u233?fnofnar a krufr\u225?tan y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Mwighayan y\u233?rsati nden\u233? t\u233?fene Yurane m\u233?taroene fifi siy\u233?m wanjargh\u233?t, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? t\u233?fene \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? f\u250?tar Fol\u233?m w\u233?i y\u233?farotam f\u233?feyot m\u233?naye k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaye nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam syaramai y\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?mo y\u233?farotam nden\u233?yameyo m\u233?inyotio y\u225?ne f\u233?rnan, korayau y\u233?nam\u233? y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rtam\u233?n. Y\u225?ne f\u233?rnan em \u225?mb yam \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? em t\u225?ik\u233?r r\u233?sagh\u233?t, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar a awanjmegh \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?ngwengotat, nden\u233? \u225?mb Buk sian k\u233?s y\u233?ngfayotat. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, f\u225? so em was\u233?rmboghan.
