Tikfaf\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f, s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, a y\u233?nd yau mat n\u233?namndang\u233?m ndern\u225?ye y\u233?nd fifi so y\u233?n\u233?m soram\u233? yuwan. W\u233?nde y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? njam Keriso n\u233?nangota w\u233?ikor, y\u233?nd so k\u233?namndang\u233?m nden\u233? f\u225? k\u233?s y\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem so tinjong\u233?m f\u225? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u225? ndern\u225?ye y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ghm\u233?gham y\u233?nd y\u233?ny\u225?tote nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Keriso k\u233?s y\u233?m nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar.
