M\u233?inyotio \u225?r emofem yaufiyam y\u233?ngwafrotat y\u233?ngrafnat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k, m\u233?nam\u233?n yaufiyam siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k rafar\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
A f\u233?m mat em nden\u233? f\u225? nufary\u233?ng m\u233?n\u225?t so tawitau t\u233?fene yaufiyam, a y\u225?faf k\u233?t\u233? yau y\u233?m yaufiyam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Efe y\u233?m y\u225?faf yau so ewafrote yaufiyam. Emo njam ewafrota yaufiyam yau yinjoi f\u225? a mat yau yiy\u225?to f\u225?.
