Tikfaf\u233? ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, yau yumyotati \u225?mb \u225?rom s\u225?i elimnda f\u233?m m\u225?m\u225?fi endm\u233?. Emo njam ewafrota n\u233?m\u233? em mbark\u225?nd f\u225? siy\u233?m mbark\u225?nd, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Keriso y\u233?m mbark\u225?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
S\u225?ifram t\u233? engwafngoi yaufiyam k\u233?tamayo r\u233?ny\u233?gh, f\u233?yo \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r efe m\u233?njt\u233? m\u233? y\u233?m yaufiyaman y\u233?m S\u225?if\u233?rene. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Ambum y\u233?nmorm\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, m\u233?n\u225?t S\u225?if\u233?rene \u225?s\u225?fogh wirorgh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u225? efe em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r yau so m\u233?njt\u233? em yaufiyaman m\u233?nam\u233?n tot\u233?r gh\u233?rs\u233? k\u233?tam\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta y\u233?m y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n, f\u225? f\u233?yotarofnar em s\u225?i m\u233?njt\u233? eng\u233?m yaufiyaman, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? t\u233? n\u233?namnday\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndfem so efandam efe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r em a efe S\u225?if\u233?rene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r em: F\u225? emofem yau ewafrotat mbark\u225?nd yau em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambum, a f\u225? emofem yau enguwetat y\u233?fene f\u250?tar\u233?f yau em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r.
