Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m watamegh f\u233?mofem \u225?rk\u233? n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd k\u233?tam\u233? r\u233?ny\u233?gh: Y\u233?nd so n\u225?uwetam t\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Yau nden\u233? em Kein efe t\u233?morw\u233?n yaufi \u225?roe tamb\u233?n a y\u233?smetam y\u225?nng\u233?n. N\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?mo y\u233?smetam krotio f\u225?? M\u233?nam\u233?n yam Kein\u233?m tawafrotau tamorw\u233?n m\u225?m\u225?fi, a yam yanngnom tawafrotau tamorw\u233?n mer.
