Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, yau t\u225?f em s\u233?lngw\u233?l njam mband marat \u225?r\u233?m m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat efandat f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?ndfem t\u233? y\u233?nfrangong\u233?m k\u233?r a t\u233? n\u233?nyawang\u233?m gh\u233?rsat m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem n\u225?uwetam t\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n, emo yau njam euweta m\u233? y\u233?m k\u233?rw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat efande yan\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f y\u233?m ngi t\u233?fn\u225?r, a f\u233?m mat em nden\u233? yau \u225?r ngi t\u233?fn\u225?rafefaf y\u233?m tuot gh\u233?rs\u233?.
