Ndenaye y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? efalo uw\u233?gh y\u233?m: Yesum y\u233?ramai y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? t\u233?feyot. F\u233?yo y\u233?ndfem w\u233?i taramang\u233?m t\u233?fene gh\u233?rs\u233? t\u233?fene f\u250?tarfet. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
W\u233?nde njam endene em f\u233?yotaroan mani m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?ngmor mer a efande yan\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f n\u225?ronjat a nakena w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t, ndern\u225?ye so norayam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene uw\u233?gh y\u233?m nden\u233? \u225?roefaf?
