Tikfaf\u233? ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, y\u233?nd yau so n\u225?uwetam m\u233? siero o k\u225?nkaye w\u233?nde m\u233?naye wafroghyame a efaloe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Ndenaye y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m efaloene, a nden\u225?ye y\u233?ndfem ewalinjotam t\u233?fene tik\u233?f Ng\u225?nj\u225?n s\u225?fr\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Ndemam\u233?n t\u233?fene mwighayam so t\u233?nmaufrong\u233? nden\u233? y\u233?ndfem tawafrotam \u225?mb yaufi, y\u233?nd w\u233?i m\u233? yau so y\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?rf\u233?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewainde t\u233?fene mwigh\u233?. F\u225? t\u233? mat y\u233?m t\u233?fenem\u233?n m\u233?inyotio.
