Tane tikfaf\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f, njam t\u233?fene tikfam yau t\u233?ny\u225?tong\u233? yaufi, y\u233?nd so y\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?rf\u233?rofnar Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene s\u225?fr\u233?re, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmaramete t\u233?fe n\u233?mat y\u233?ndfem y\u233?ngwamnendam m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem ewaitatam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k a ewafrotam n\u233?m\u233? yam \u225?uw\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?m\u233?inde f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
A y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m y\u225?ne n\u225?k: nden\u233? y\u233?ndfem so efalo yiy\u225?totam y\u225?njo Ambum Yesu Kerisoene y\u233?tkw\u233?n, a n\u225?uwetam t\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?mo y\u233?nmaramai t\u233?fe n\u225?k. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u225? emofem ewaitotat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k emor y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?n, a f\u225? y\u233?m y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n. A nden\u225?ye y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? f\u225? y\u233?mor t\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n, y\u233?nd mat n\u225?y\u225?totam m\u233?n\u225?yan Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?mo y\u233?nmaramai t\u233?fe.
