Tikfaf\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f, yau t\u225?f efalo ey\u225?totati m\u233?inyotio mb\u233?rmb\u233?r, w\u233?nde eufotati mb\u233?rmb\u233?r m\u233?n\u225?t fandagh\u233?t n\u233?m\u233? f\u225? f\u233?t\u233? em Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta, m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u225?rf\u225?r uny\u233?gh mat y\u225?togh \u225?r t\u233? engmorm\u233?n mband maratot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m nden\u225?ye f\u233?mofem so tayamngongi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r: \u193?rk\u233? \u225?r njam noraya nden\u233? Yesu Keriso t\u233? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n fifie f\u225? fiy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
