Tikfaf\u233? ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, f\u233?m em Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta a t\u233? ewainday\u233?nd f\u225?, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? efe y\u233?m f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u225?inde efe y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
