W\u233?nde y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene, a f\u225? efe mat em Ng\u225?nj\u225?n n\u225?y\u225?retat t\u233?fefaf, w\u233?nde f\u225? efe yau em Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta yau n\u225?y\u225?retat t\u233?fefaf. Ndenaye y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m mb\u233?rmb\u233?r \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m efaloe a mb\u233?rmb\u233?r \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m uny\u233?ghe.
