Tikfaf\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?nd so n\u225?uwetam t\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n uw\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta. M\u233?inyotio \u225?r emo euwete t\u233? n\u233?namnde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambum a mat y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Emo yau njam euweta yau mat y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n siy\u233?m uw\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Ndenaye Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yuyafotam y\u225?njo uw\u233?gh t\u233?feyot: Y\u233?mo y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam y\u225?njo m\u233? y\u233?naro Ambum y\u233?n\u233? mband maratot m\u233?n\u225?t t\u233?fene so y\u233?m gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m efalofifi uw\u233?gh: yau y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fene uw\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?neyot, y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene uw\u233?gh t\u233?feyot m\u233?n\u225?yan y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam y\u225?njo Ambum m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u233?morw\u233?n krufr\u225?t gh\u233?ng\u233?n s\u225?i tawitau t\u233?fene yaufiyam.
