Tikfaf\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f, njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmuwetam y\u233?nd mindefifi w\u233?i nden\u233?yameyo so n\u225?uwetam t\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
\u193?mb \u225?rom yau yinjoi Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, w\u233?nde njam y\u233?nd n\u225?uwetam t\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?mor t\u233?fefaf, a y\u225?ne uw\u233?gh k\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar t\u233?fefaf.
