Y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?nd y\u233?nmor Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene k\u233?nj\u250?n a f\u225? y\u233?mor t\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mo t\u233? y\u233?nmaramai t\u233?fe y\u225?njo Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
