Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r\u233?m t\u233? em\u233?indat f\u233?m afalogh\u233?t, efe elimndat y\u233?fenjo fifi m\u233?ndeyam, endefefaf yau y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r.
