a kawerangi f\u233?myo k\u233?t\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene uw\u233?ghan, njamandio f\u233?m nawanjetati t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisoene gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisat s\u225?i tawaramang\u233? f\u233?fe tuot gh\u233?rs\u233?.
