Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Jon, f\u233?fene m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n. M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m Yesuene lim\u225?n\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n, y\u233?ndfem y\u233?rsam k\u233?rt\u233? a t\u233?krat. F\u233?yo, y\u233?nd so y\u233?n\u233?m muyaf\u233? a m\u233?tar, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yesum so y\u233?nm\u225?ut\u225?ne. Y\u233?nd k\u233?t\u233? kw\u233?morw\u233?n Fatmos f\u233?ran, m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233? t\u225?itotaw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a Yesuenem\u233?n si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
