nden\u233? norayai, "Efarota bukan n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mon efande, a tangwatemb 7 Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?nfaf: k\u233?t\u225?n Efesos, S\u233?mirna, Fegamo, Taiatira, Sadis, Filadelfia a k\u233?t\u225?n Laodikia."
