Y\u233?nd n\u233?ngawengoy\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t so tinjongay\u233?n efe norayau tafaf. Njam s\u233?mta nawengoy\u233?n y\u233?ndo ewinjoy\u233?n 7 wakayoghkaf gol lambef\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
a y\u233?n\u233? lambef\u233? wakayogh n\u233?ndk\u233?f fifiyan y\u233?ndo yinjoy\u233?n ndenanit \u193?roene Ambum, tawong\u233?rw\u233?n tomb\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me k\u233?t\u225?notio kafkaf a golm\u233?n beles t\u233?farng\u233?rw\u233?n w\u233?fam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u225?ne s\u233?nko s\u233?f tamorw\u233?n kwayagharo ndenanit kafe s\u233?fnit, o \u225?s fifinit, a y\u225?ne gh\u233?k\u233?f k\u225?netaw\u233?t f\u233?s kankanit. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
