Y\u225?ne tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ngaye taweretau 7 k\u233?nd, a y\u225?ne mb\u237?rmb\u237?rta n\u233?ngtory\u233?ng witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?if\u233?, a y\u225?ne s\u225?f k\u225?l\u225?lau ndenanit sotaf\u233? efogh y\u233?nau nanete. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?ndo njam yinjoy\u233?n, y\u233?nd nuy\u225?y\u233?n y\u225?ne kafkafot k\u233?r \u225?rnit. Y\u233?mon efayoi y\u225?njo tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ng\u233? a korayang\u233?, "Yau f\u233?rf\u233?r n\u233?m! Y\u233?nd w\u233?m fronde a soram\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?nd w\u233?m efe gh\u233?rs\u233? w\u233?m! Efe k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n a s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd gh\u233?rs\u233? w\u233?m tuot! Tafaf em ki k\u233?rm\u233?n a f\u233?sm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n efarota f\u233?mon n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? efande, s\u233?nonjo n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m a n\u233?m\u233? so n\u233?ngufrotat soram\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
7 k\u233?nd t\u233?noghm\u233?n yam y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?mon k\u233?s tafande tane tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ngata, a w\u233?i 7 wakayoghkaf gol lambef\u233? y\u233?n\u233? em: 7 k\u233?nd k\u233?s em njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r y\u233?n\u233? fem 7 Yesuene m\u233?rnot, a 7 lambef\u233? wakayoghm\u233?n k\u233?s em 7 Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? fem.
