\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Y\u233?n\u233? si siy\u233?m y\u225? tamb\u233?n emo ew\u233?rete 7 k\u233?nd y\u225?njo tamb\u233?n ngangaye, a f\u225? efe tiotau y\u233?nam\u233? 7 gol lambef\u233? wakayoghm\u233?n sifayam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
