F\u233?m t\u233? m\u233?tare tam t\u233?kr\u225?tam\u233? tayot \u233?kmboghofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
W\u233?nde tane \u225?w\u225?taran\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf: f\u233?mofem yau wuwetati y\u233?nd nden\u233? fronde k\u233?s tamorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Kemnangi nder\u233? nayu f\u233?m t\u233? nuyangi fronde f\u233?fenjo uw\u233?ghta! K\u233?nawengongi tafaf w\u233?ikor a n\u225?s\u225?fotati nden\u233? fronde ndern\u225?ye k\u225?s\u225?fotaw\u233?t. Yau njam f\u233?mofem yafrotati, y\u233?nd so w\u233?n\u233?m tawit\u233?rmbon lambef\u233? wakayoghm\u233?n y\u233?fenjo sifayata m\u233?inyotio Yesuene m\u233?rnam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m mer f\u233?fenem\u233?n: f\u233?mofem m\u233?ndefnar y\u233?fandati Nikolait m\u233?rnafene m\u225?m\u225?fi yam wafrogh, y\u233?ndon w\u233?i nden\u225?yo.
