\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo m\u233?k k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n njafaran. Maik\u233?l a y\u225?njoyo njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rf\u233? k\u225?smetaw\u233?t ndimbal fuwayaf\u233? a ndimbal fuwayoene si r\u233?sagh \u225?rf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde ndimbal fuwai yau kor muyaf\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n, a y\u233?mofem y\u233?tarnam\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo sifay\u233? k\u233?t\u233? njafaran. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal fuwai y\u233?nmitam\u233?nd yuwot, y\u233?n\u233? t\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r kamban y\u233?mndetat Defol, o S\u225?if\u233?r, emo elimnd\u233? uny\u233?ghe m\u233?inyotio \u225?r mband maratan. F\u225? t\u233? y\u233?nmitam\u233?nd mband maratot y\u225?njo si r\u233?sagh \u225?rf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?nd n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?n ndimbal ke njafarta k\u233?norayau, "S\u233?nonjo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene wanjar\u233?gh t\u233? nufar! S\u233?nonjo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? yuyafo y\u225?njo waft\u233? nden\u233? Warsagh \u225?r! S\u233?nonjo y\u225?ne Kerisom yuyafo y\u225?ne muy\u233?. M\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?r emo tawawafrotau s\u233?nk\u233?r efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?t efogh a s\u233?mb\u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene s\u225?fr\u233?re, njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?nmitam\u233?nd yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?m y\u225?inday\u233?nd Sif tosane f\u233?rke a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si waitoghe, a y\u233?mofem yau y\u233?fenjo gh\u233?rs\u233? t\u225?uwetaw\u233?t mindefifi w\u233?nde f\u233?rf\u233?rofnar tamorw\u233?n krot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde n\u225?uwetati, f\u233?m njafar a f\u233?m efe em k\u233?t\u233?! W\u233?nde gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? mband maratoe a arakaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n S\u225?if\u233?r t\u233? t\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?fefaf, f\u225? siy\u233?m n\u233?kw afoghkaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? mat y\u233?m y\u225?ne kw\u233?f nd\u233?mbnd\u233?mb t\u233? namndangi."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Njam ndimbal fuwayam yinjoi nden\u233? f\u225? t\u233? y\u233?nmitam\u233?nd mband maratot. F\u233?yo y\u233?mo t\u233?ronjau amaf emo y\u233?r\u225?ftam ghak\u233?r ambum. F\u225? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n t\u233?smangai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? amafoe yaramay\u233?nd ndimbal ndikakane s\u243?mbio njamb, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? so kanefetau y\u225?ne freng\u233?ghkaf sifayafaf fanfne yuwot, \u225?nde f\u225? so tambetaw\u233?t nambio yunj\u233?f a mbarmbar k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?n\u233? kambanoeta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
A w\u233?i y\u233?n\u233? kambanam s\u233?nf\u233?ne tamb\u233?n y\u233?nmetoi amafoefaf nu ndenanit wanje, m\u233?n\u225?t amaf so k\u233?f\u233?ram tanangai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
W\u233?nde amaf y\u225?ut\u225?nam mband maratam. Mband maratam y\u225?njo s\u233?nf\u233?ne y\u233?saw\u233?ry\u233?ng a n\u233?loi nu \u225?rk\u233? nu ndimbal fuwayam t\u233? y\u233?nmetoi y\u225?njo s\u233?nf\u233?neta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u233?yo ndimbal fuwai n\u233?kw t\u233?morw\u233?n amafoefaf a nuwanoi a m\u233?k y\u233?funai y\u225?ne ambumafefaf, m\u233?inyotio emofem efalo ey\u225?totat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k a naweretat Yesuene sian. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
A ndimbal fuwai nokayoi arakaf t\u233?ndon.
