\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ndimbal g\u225?si\u233? n\u233?nurtoi arakafta
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon yinjoy\u233?n ndimbal g\u225?si\u233? n\u233?nurtoi arakafta. K\u233?t\u233? tamorw\u233?n 10 tartar a 7 s\u233?nko a \u225?kiki tafayong\u233?rw\u233?n m\u233?inyotio tartaram\u233?, a f\u233?natayero s\u233?nkoyam\u233? yaufi y\u233?tkw\u233?n tawakayong\u233?rw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Ndimbal g\u225?si\u233? y\u233?ndon \u225?rk\u233? yinjoy\u233?n k\u233?retau ndenanit f\u233?nat\u233? s\u225?fot ndimbal munjan fus y\u233?tkw\u233?n lef\u233?d, w\u233?nde tamorw\u233?n kafkaf ndenanit k\u233?ghat ndimbal w\u233?r\u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Beya a s\u233?nf\u233?ne ndenanit ndimbal munjan fus. Ndimbal fuwayam yaramai ndimbal g\u225?siyai y\u225?njo waft\u233? a y\u225?njo lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? a ndimbal muy\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
\u193?mb ndimbal g\u225?siane s\u233?nkoyan mbor k\u233?retau ndenanit kar y\u233?smetam\u233?nd fronde, a y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rm\u233?n mbor mer n\u233?namndai. M\u233?inyotio mband marat s\u233?lngw\u233?l tamorw\u233?n a t\u225?itotaw\u233?t ndimbal g\u225?si\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
\u193?r\u233?m t\u225?wefnotaw\u233?t ndimbal fuwaye m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mon t\u233? yaramai y\u225?njo muy\u233? ndimbal g\u225?siyai. Y\u233?mofem w\u233?i t\u225?wefnotaw\u233?t ndimbal g\u225?siyai, korayaw\u233?t, "Efe nden\u233? y\u233?m ndimbal g\u225?si\u233?? Emo so m\u233?k t\u233?funang\u233? y\u225?faf?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yumyoi ndimbal g\u225?si\u233? siot s\u225?i korayau yaufi si Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf, a y\u225?yot yaramai muy\u233? wafrogh\u233?t f\u225? n\u233?m\u233? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n 42 gh\u233?rareyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u225? korayau sotaf\u233? yaufi si Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf, a tas\u233?rmbotau y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?n a y\u225?ne \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? a y\u233?fefaf w\u233?i nden\u225?yo efe emor njafaran. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam waft\u233? yaramai Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?rf\u233? \u225?sm\u233?gh\u233?t a s\u225?i tawaindang\u233? f\u225?. A yaramai waft\u233? m\u233?inyotio \u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t, m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?n, f\u233?nat\u233? si t\u233?f\u233?n \u225?r, ndimbal yum\u233?n \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
M\u233?inyotio \u225?r efe em y\u233?n\u233? mband maratm\u233?n so y\u225?wefnotat ndimbal g\u225?siyai. W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r endefene y\u233?tkw\u233?n em Sif tasane gh\u233?rs\u233? bukan, y\u233?mofem yau so y\u225?wefnotat. Sif tosam y\u233?tkw\u233?n ewafarotam y\u233?n\u233? efalo y\u225?togh \u225?rfene y\u225?njo bukan frondeyo soram\u233? mband marat nufrotam. F\u225? y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m Sif tos\u233? \u225?r\u233?m efe y\u233?smetam\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u225? efe y\u233?m t\u233?nganaf\u233?, so f\u233?t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?rete! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Efe njam t\u233? ew\u233?retat kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngot so f\u233?t\u233? em kw\u233?fkw\u233?f \u225?r. Efe njam esmetat krot witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naifaye so f\u233?t\u233? esmetat witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naifaye. Y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m nden\u233? efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r t\u225?f so em m\u233?tar a muyaf\u233?. Y\u233?mofem t\u225?f so m\u233? efalo yiy\u225?totat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 \u193?mb ndimbal g\u225?si\u233? n\u233?ntory\u233?ng mband marat tamb\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon yinjoy\u233?n \u225?mb ndimbal g\u225?si\u233? k\u233?ntonau mband marat tamb\u233?n. F\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u243?mbio tartaraf\u233? ndenanit Sif tos\u233?, w\u233?nde f\u225? korayau ndenanit ndimbal fuwai kar t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?mo tawafrotau m\u233?inyotio muy\u233? frondem\u233?n ndimbal g\u225?siane s\u225?fr\u233?re, a y\u233?m\u233?indai mband marat a y\u225?njo \u225?r w\u225?wefnogh\u233?t fronde ndimbal g\u225?si\u233?, efe t\u233? k\u233?r k\u233?nj\u250?ta mer n\u225?y\u225?toi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
A y\u233?mon tawafrotau ndimbal s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? ufarogh yam, t\u233?funau f\u233?s k\u233?natarnaw\u233?t njafarta mband maratot \u225?r gh\u233?kfan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? ufarogh yam t\u233?fnan y\u225?yot waft\u233? yaramay\u233?nd m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tafrotau fronde ndimbal g\u225?siane muw\u233?muwaye. Y\u233?mo tamndetau m\u233?inyotio \u225?r mband maratan m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mofem so tafrotaw\u233?t mbanmban ndimbal g\u225?siai utman\u233?gh\u233?t efe t\u233? y\u233?smetam\u233?nd witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naifaye a w\u233?nde mer w\u233?i n\u233?namndai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?namayom\u233?n ndimbal g\u225?siai yaramay\u233?nd waft\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i taramangai ambone fronde ndimbal g\u225?siane mbanmbanoe, m\u233?n\u225?t ndimbal g\u225?siane mbanmban so korayau krot ekmeta y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emofem yau njam y\u225?wefnotat mbanmbanoe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?mo w\u233?i w\u225?faregh ewafngoi m\u233?inyotio \u225?r, n\u233?mbnar k\u233?t\u225?n ndimbal, wem\u225?r a yauyau, yuwek a orsagh \u225?r, m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tarsaw\u233?t mbor y\u233?fene tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ngayan o s\u225?f sotan, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?mb yau so rokar manie erse o et\u233?rne maniot t\u225?fandro njam y\u233?n\u233? mboraf\u233? y\u233?m, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m ndimbal g\u225?siane y\u233?tkw\u233?n o y\u225?ne waf\u233?gh y\u233?tkw\u233?n.
