F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon yinyoy\u233?n Sif tos\u233? takayong\u233?rw\u233?n Jaion mband tunakfan, m\u233?rne y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?rf\u233? 144,000 m\u233?inyotio efe tamorw\u233?n y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?naf\u233? a Y\u225?refane y\u233?tkw\u233?naf\u233? takayong\u233?rw\u233?n y\u233?fene s\u225?f sotan {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
A y\u233?ndon n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?n ke njafarta ndenanit t\u225?rf\u225?r w\u233?r\u233?r nu y\u233?nau nasunat o ndimbal toy\u233? kenit. Ndenanit t\u233?morw\u233?n t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r kembnem\u233?n wagh rokare y\u233?nau nambnat m\u233?rne. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
A y\u233?mofem t\u233?rametaw\u233?t tot\u233?r wagh lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? r\u233?re a 4 akegh gh\u233?rsaf\u233? w\u233?r\u225?r a s\u233?nko \u225?rfene r\u233?re. \u193?rk\u233? \u225?r yau so kotametau y\u233?n\u233? wagh, w\u233?nde m\u233? f\u225?ro 144,000 \u225?rro mat tamorw\u233?n efe t\u233? ewafery\u233?ng y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u225? y\u233?n\u233? em efe yau kawas\u233?rmbotat amafaf\u233?, f\u225? m\u233? m\u233?inyo em. Y\u233?mofem t\u225?itotat Sif tos\u233? \u225?rkam\u233? f\u225? tiota. F\u225? y\u233?n\u233? wanjar\u233?ghkaf em \u225?r tamb\u233?n, \u225?rk\u233? em frondembwe Ng\u225?nj\u225?neyot a Sif tosai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
N\u233?m\u233? uny\u233?gh yau ewawinjoy\u233?nd y\u233?fene mb\u237?rmb\u237?ran, f\u225? sem t\u233?fnofnar.
