F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon yinjoy\u233?n \u225?mb njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r kanefetau njafar tukma, a y\u225?faf t\u233?morw\u233?n akegh mer si s\u225?i t\u233?ngwaitotau y\u233?fefaf m\u233? efe \u225?r y\u233?morare y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan, m\u233?inyotio ndimbal yu, m\u233?r\u233?n, a f\u233?nat\u233? si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
