Y\u225?ne gh\u233?k\u233?f em ndenanit f\u233?s k\u225?nk\u233?k\u225?nk\u233?, a y\u225?ne s\u233?nkoyan tafayong\u233?rw\u233?n t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?kiki. F\u233?r\u233?n takayong\u233?rw\u233?n y\u225?faf, \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r yau mat em y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n w\u233?nde m\u233? f\u225?ro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
