Njafarm\u233?n fiyaram t\u225?itotaw\u233?t f\u225?, k\u233?rsau kwayagh\u233? osan a tawong\u233?rw\u233?n mer s\u225?l\u225?me, kwayagh\u233? a nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u225?ne s\u233?nf\u233?neta y\u233?n\u233?m witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?if\u233?, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?naye so yirone ndimbal yu. Y\u233?mo so elimnde warsagh \u225?roene tot t\u233?f\u233?n w\u233?tue. Y\u233?mon so etumnde w\u233?ri nu wafroghm\u233?n rokaran M\u233?inyotio waft\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene yaufiyaufi n\u233?kwe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u225?ne s\u225?l\u225?meyan a buraburan f\u233?r\u233?n takayong\u233?rw\u233?n, "Warsagh \u225?rfene Warsagh \u225?r a yurafene Yur\u233?."
