F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon yinjoy\u233?n ndimbal kwayagh\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? a f\u225? efe t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233?. Mband marat a njafar nawaindangeyay\u233?nd y\u225?ne s\u225?fr\u233?re, a y\u233?feyot \u225?mb sifay\u233? yau t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
