Arakafam en\u233?miyoi m\u233?inyotio k\u233?r \u225?r efe k\u233?t\u233? tamorw\u233?n y\u225?ne w\u233?rghan. K\u233?r a k\u233?r \u225?rfene sifay\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?n Ades en\u233?miyoi m\u233?inyotio k\u233?r \u225?r efe k\u233?t\u233? tamorw\u233?n w\u233?i. F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam moghan ekmai \u225?r f\u233?nataf\u233?nataye. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewinjoi n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mofem t\u233? tawafrotaw\u233?t a y\u233?mo mwigh\u233? ekmai n\u233?m\u233? mbark\u225?nd t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?yo k\u233?r a Ades ewitam k\u233?nj\u250?t marataye f\u233?s\u233?t. Y\u233?n\u233? marataye f\u233?s siy\u233?m y\u233?namayo k\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
