F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon ewinjeyay\u233?n tot\u233?r njafar a tot\u233?r mband marat. Fronde njafar a fronde mband marat t\u233? nawaindangeyay\u233?nd, a arakaf yau k\u233?t\u233? nafrangoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?ndon yinjoy\u233?n Nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar ndimbal tesen, tot\u233?r Jerusalem, k\u233?newonau njafarta Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne tamb\u233?n, afreng\u233?ghare sariaf\u233? umaneghkaf amafnit y\u225?njo \u225?roe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
A y\u233?ndon n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?n ndimbal ke k\u233?tam\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifayata k\u233?norayau, "S\u233?nonjo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?ngo siy\u233?m y\u225?njo \u225?rf\u233?! F\u225? so emor y\u233?maf\u233?, a f\u225? so em y\u225?ne \u225?r. Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u225? f\u225?yo so y\u233?m y\u233?maf\u233?, a so y\u233?m y\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?mon so m\u233?inyotio yengam ewaw\u225?ny\u225?nyote y\u233?fene gh\u233?k\u233?fta. K\u233?t\u233? yau so y\u233?m k\u233?r, w\u233?ikor gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? o ye o nd\u233?mke, m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r yam t\u233? nawaindangi."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u225? efe t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifayan norayai, "Y\u233?ndon s\u233?nonjo m\u233?inyotio rokar yiy\u225?totan tot\u233?r!" W\u233?i norayai tafaf, "Y\u233?farota y\u233?n\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? si sem ndimbal mwighaf\u233? em a efalo." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
A f\u225? norayai tafaf, "T\u233?fe nufrote! Y\u233?nd w\u233?m fronde a soram\u233?, r\u233?ny\u233?gh a wifogh. Y\u225?yot efe nuam y\u233?ramete y\u233?ndon so taraman nu n\u233?net faiofnaye k\u233?tam\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? w\u233?r\u233?r nu tamb\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u225? efe em waing\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?mofem so tawanangi y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio: y\u233?nd so w\u233?m y\u225?ne Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, a f\u225? so em tane ambum. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?rf\u233?rro \u225?r, s\u233?n ram\u233?gh \u225?r, ndimbal mwigh\u233? t\u225?ran\u233?gh \u225?r, \u225?r ngi t\u233?fn\u225?r, yaufi wal t\u233?fn\u225?r, a f\u225? efe em f\u233?nataf\u233?nat\u233? ghar yam wafrogh \u225?r, mewang w\u225?wefnogh \u225?r a m\u233?inyotio uny\u233?gh \u225?r- y\u233?fene sifay\u233? s\u225?i y\u233?m f\u233?s a r\u233?m\u233?r\u233?m\u233? w\u233?kw\u233?r akrar\u233?gh sifay\u233?, y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m y\u233?namayo k\u233?r."
