\u193?mb 7m\u233?n njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r emo taweretau 7 dis afoghare soramam\u233?n f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? yam y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a norayai tafaf, "K\u233?naf, y\u233?ndon so k\u233?nmauyafon tot\u233?r awer\u233?gh amaf, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m Sif tosane amaf." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
A y\u233?mo w\u233?ngwanai y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re k\u233?t\u225?n minde tuk\u233?n mband tunak\u233?f tuk\u233?t, a kwauyafotau Nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar ndimbal tesen, Jerusalem, k\u233?newonau k\u233?tam\u233? njafarta Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne tamb\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
T\u233?morw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ndimbal kwayaghaf\u233?, a y\u225?ne \u225?l\u225?lagh t\u233?morw\u233?n ndenanit mer sariaf\u233? w\u237?m, kwayagh\u233? a glasro w\u237?mm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
T\u233?morw\u233?n w\u237?m \u225?r\u225?ke minde tukm\u233? 12 s\u233?safnef\u233? tamorw\u233?n 12 njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r s\u233?safne f\u233?yotaro. Y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?safneyan y\u233?tkw\u233?n takayong\u233?rw\u233?n y\u233?fene 12 Israilm\u233?n m\u233?r\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
K\u233?t\u233? tamorw\u233?n nambio s\u233?safne wer tamb\u233?n, nambio yamb\u233?rm\u233? tamb\u233?n, nambio n\u225?ik\u225?i tamb\u233?n, a nambioyo mbormbor tamb\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal tesenoene w\u237?m \u225?r\u225?ke stamorw\u233?n 12 w\u237?maf\u233?, a k\u233?t\u233? tafayong\u233?rw\u233?n 12 Sif tosane muyaf\u233? \u225?rfene y\u233?tkw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r efe norayai tafaf teretau golm\u233?n ufogh w\u233?tu ndimbul m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tufotau y\u233?n\u233? tesen, y\u225?ne s\u233?safne, a w\u237?m \u225?r\u225?ke. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Tesen t\u233?morw\u233?n tomb\u233? a marat f\u233?yotaro t\u233?morw\u233?n ndenaro. Y\u233?mo tufotau ndimbal tesen y\u233?n\u233? ufogh w\u233?tu ndimbule a yinjoi nden\u233? 2,200 kilomit\u233? yu tomb\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n, nden\u233?yameyo marat a nden\u233?yameyo tuk. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?mon tufotau y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r\u225?ke t\u233?ndo, a t\u233?morw\u233?n nden\u233? 65 mit\u233? s\u233?njt\u233?, \u225?rfene ufogh yame \u225?rk\u233? njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rom tafrotau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r\u225?ke t\u233?morw\u233?n mer kwayagh\u233? w\u237?mm\u233?n, a ndimbal tesen t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233? merfifi golm\u233?nro, ndenanit glas. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Ndimbal tesenm\u233?n \u225?r\u225?ke wer\u233?gh t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n w\u237?m stamorw\u233?n wamaneghkaf f\u233?nataye m\u233?ndef\u233? w\u237?me. Fronde wer\u233?gh t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n w\u237?m t\u233?morw\u233?n jasfam\u233?n, y\u233?n\u233?mayom\u233?n safair\u233?m\u233?n, nambiom\u233?n ageitm\u233?n, 4m\u233?n emeraldm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
5m\u233?n oniks, 6m\u233?n kanalian, 7m\u233?n krisolit, 8m\u233?n beril, 9m\u233?n tofaj, 1om\u233?n krisofrase, 11m\u233?n jasint, a 12m\u233?n ametist. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
12 s\u233?safne stamorw\u233?n 12 ndindinit f\u233?r\u233?nf\u233?rnaf\u233?; f\u233?natayero s\u233?safne stamorw\u233?n \u225?mbiro ndindi mbwe ngarot. A ndimbal tesenoene end t\u233?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n m\u233? golro, ndenanit glas.
