Y\u233?ndon yau yinjoy\u233?n w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal tesenan, m\u233?nam\u233?n Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n M\u233?inyotio Waftaf\u233? a Sif tos\u233? f\u225? sere y\u233?fene w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal tesenan yau efogh a gh\u233?rare so nan\u233?t k\u233?t\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ndimbal kwayagham so y\u233?ramete kwayagh\u233?, a Sif tos\u233? f\u225? y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m lambef\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Ndimbal yum\u233?n \u225?r so eyota y\u225?ne kwayaghan, a mband maratm\u233?n warsagh \u225?r\u233?m so en\u233?rsat y\u233?fenjo ndimbal kwayagh\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Efghon yau s\u233?safne so namnat, m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? yau s\u233?mb\u225?r y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
M\u233?inyotio ndimbal yuam so en\u233?rsat y\u233?fenjo ndimbal kwayagh\u233? a utman\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal tesenfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
W\u233?nde n\u233?m\u233? yaufi yau so k\u233?nyawang\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n, yau y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emofem ewafrotat w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? yam o uny\u233?ghe, w\u233?nde m\u233? f\u225?ro endefene y\u233?tkw\u233?n ekai Sif tosane gh\u233?rs\u233? bukan.
