F\u233?yo njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rom kwauyafotau gh\u233?rsam\u233?n nuaf\u233? wanje, m\u233? glasro, t\u233?nf\u233?ronau k\u233?tam\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifayata a Sif tosata {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
k\u233?t\u233? n\u233?ndk\u233?fan y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal endm\u233? y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal tesenan, a wanje witmawitm\u233? kar\u233?fam\u233? tayang\u233?rw\u233?n gh\u233?rsam\u233?n w\u233?n, kafotaw\u233?t 12 f\u233?nat\u233? w\u233?n mbwe s\u225?f, afogh w\u233?n mbwe y\u225?fene t\u233?morw\u233?n t\u250?m\u233?n gh\u233?rareye. A y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?nafene arau sem mer \u225?y\u225?togh\u233?t em m\u233?inyotio ndimbal yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
K\u233?t\u233? yau so y\u233?m wafalngogh. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? a Sif tosane utman\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? so y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal tesenan, a y\u225?ne faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u233?m so y\u225?wefnotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?mofem so y\u233?fandat y\u225?ne s\u225?f, a y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?n so em faroghkaf y\u233?fene s\u225?f sotan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
K\u233?t\u233? yau so y\u233?m s\u233?mb\u225?r. Y\u233?mofem yau so n\u225?ronjat lambef\u233? kwayagh\u233? o efogh kwayagh\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n so y\u233?m y\u233?fene kwayagh\u233?. A y\u233?mofem so y\u233?limndat tuot.
