"Kor aem! Y\u233?nd n\u233?nangotan tekofnar! Freng\u233?ghkaf y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r y\u233?m emo erete afrogh si y\u233?n\u233? Bukan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?nd, Jon, y\u233?n\u233? fw\u233?m efe k\u225?y\u225?retau a tafandau y\u233?n\u233? yam. A y\u233?ndon njam k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?n a tafandaw\u233?n, y\u233?nd nuy\u225?y\u233?n w\u225?wefnogh\u233?t njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?roene kafkafot emo tauyafotau y\u233?n\u233? yam tafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? norayai tafaf, "Yau y\u233?n\u233? yafrota! Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?m k\u233?s n\u233?m a fene f\u250?t\u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? m\u233?inyotio emo efalo yiy\u225?tota n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? efarotam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? bukan. Y\u225?wefnota Ng\u225?nj\u225?netro!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
A f\u225? norayai tafaf, "Yau yamnda kwankwane y\u233?n\u233? yam ufroghm\u233?n si y\u233?n\u233? bukan, m\u233?nam\u233?n efogh kaka n\u233?n\u225?y\u225?tote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u225? emo ewafrote yaufi, m\u233? a ewafrota yaufi. F\u225? efe y\u233?m awas\u233?rmboghan, m\u233? a y\u233?m awas\u233?rmboghan. F\u225? emo ewafrote mer yam m\u233? a ewarota mer yam, a f\u225? efe y\u233?m nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar, m\u233? a y\u233?m nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar."
