"Kor aem! Y\u233?nd n\u233?nangotan tekofnar! Tane fai sem tafaf em a y\u233?ndon so ewarametan f\u233?natayero m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mofem t\u233? tawafrotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Alfa a Omega, Fronde a Soram\u233?, R\u233?ny\u233?gh a Wifogh.
